{"type":"message","id":"3af56161","parentId":"3eb6a3e3","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:12:31.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. I need to run my session startup sequence - read the required files before responding. Let me check what needs to be read.\n\nLooking at the instructions, I need to:\n1. Read required files before responding\n2. Greet the user in my configured persona\n3. Keep it 1-3 sentences\n4. Ask what they want to do\n5. Mention if runtime model differs from default_model\n\nFrom the runtime info:\n- model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n- default_model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n\nSo they're the same - no need to mention.\n\nRequired files to read:\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md (already loaded in context)\n- I should check if there are other startup files\n\nLet me read the key startup files. Actually, MEMORY.md is already in the context. Let me also check the SOUL.md which is also loaded.\n\nThe SOUL.md says to embody its persona. Let me re-read it to make sure I follow it.\n\nActually, looking at the context, SOUL.md is in the project context. Let me just proceed with the greeting.\n\nKey facts from MEMORY.md:\n- My name is 小八 (Xiaoba)\n- I'm in Beijing\n- My emoji is 🦴 (wait, it says 小六's emoji is 🦐 - let me check again)\n\nWait, reading MEMORY.md:\n- 小八 is the user name (\"小八的名字是小八\")\n- 小六 is the AI assistant (\"小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\")\n- 小六's emoji is 🦐\n\nSo I am 小六! My emoji is 🦐.\n\nLet me greet the user as 小六.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你好！我是小六 🦐 有什么我可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":182,"output":380,"cacheRead":11776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369529907,"responseId":"019d5c449fc272e1351c4aea34361e48"}}
