{"type":"message","id":"ee530930","parentId":"8d0ff216","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:16:18.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现了一个问题：\n\n1. **task-weight-estimator** 和 **vector-memory** 这两个技能只有 SKILL.md 文件，没有实际的 JavaScript 实现代码！\n\n这意味着这两个技能目前是\"空壳\" - 只有描述文档，没有实际可执行的代码。这可能是一个问题。\n\n让我汇总检查结果给用户。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 📋 技能全面检查报告\n\n| 技能 | 文件 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **task_orchestrator** | skill.js ✅ | ⚠️ 需验证 | 有主逻辑，但 scripts/ 为空 |\n| **github-manager** | skill + 3 脚本 ✅ | ✅ 完整 | 含 code-review、changelog、project-manager |\n| **task-weight-estimator** | 仅 SKILL.md | ❌ **空壳** | 无 .js 实际代码 |\n| **vector-memory** | 仅 SKILL.md | ❌ **空壳** | 无 .js 实际代码 |\n\n**⚠️ 问题**：`task-weight-estimator` 和 `vector-memory` 只有文档描述，缺少执行代码，无法真正工作。\n\n需要我修复这两个技能吗？还是先了解它们应该实现什么功能？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":470,"output":247,"cacheRead":16512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369760645,"responseId":"019d5c482532d3a421d51952d19c24ca"}}
{"type":"message","id":"05d210fa","parentId":"ee530930","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:19:18.787Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 14:19 GMT+8] 学习、修复：# OpenClaw 技能体系全面优化报告（五维最优解）\n\n> 基于您提供的“技能全面检查报告”，我们从 **科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性** 五个维度对现有四个技能进行评估，并针对 `task-weight-estimator` 和 `vector-memory` 两个空壳技能给出完整的伪代码实现。 \n> 同时，整合之前对话中的最佳实践（评分路由、上下文保护、子代理进度），形成一套可立即投产的技能体系。\n\n---\n\n## 一、技能现状五维评估\n\n| 技能 | 科学性 | 鲁棒性 | 灵活性 | 可嵌入性 | 效率性 | 综合评分 | 问题 |\n|------|--------|--------|--------|----------|--------|----------|------|\n| **task_orchestrator** | ✅ 高（多维度评分+上下文保护） | ✅ 高（心跳、超时、重试） | ✅ 高（可配置） | ✅ 高（hooks） | ⚠️ 中（未拆分脚本） | 4.5/5 | `scripts/` 目录为空，可拆分辅助脚本 |\n| **github-manager** | ✅ 高（API 封装合理） | ✅ 高（错误重试） | ✅ 高（多操作） | ✅ 高 | ✅ 高 | 5/5 | 完整 |\n| **task-weight-estimator** | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | 0/5 | 无代码 |\n| **vector-memory** | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | ❌ 空壳 | 0/5 | 无代码 |\n\n**结论**：需要立即补全 `task-weight-estimator` 和 `vector-memory`，并优化 `task_orchestrator` 的模块化拆分。\n\n---\n\n## 二、补全技能设计与五维最优实现\n\n### 2.1 `task-weight-estimator` —— 独立的任务评分引擎\n\n**设计目标**：提供纯粹的任务复杂度与不确定性评估，供 `task_orchestrator` 及其他技能调用。\n\n#### 五维设计\n\n| 维度 | 实现 |\n|------|------|\n| 科学性 | 基于命令数量、网络/交互特征量化评分（0-6分），映射到权重 0-10，与路由建议对应。 |\n| 鲁棒性 | 输入异常（非字符串）返回默认值；正则匹配失败降级为 0 分；所有正则表达式预编译。 |\n| 灵活性 | 支持用户通过环境变量覆盖评分阈值；提供 `evaluate` 纯函数，无副作用。 |\n| 可嵌入性 | 独立技能，可通过 `require` 或 hooks 被其他技能调用。 |\n| 效率性 | O(n) 复杂度，n 为命令串长度；正则匹配一次完成，无额外 I/O。 |\n\n#### 完整伪代码\n\n```javascript\n// ~/.openclaw/skills/task-weight-estimator/skill.js\nconst COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS = [1, 5, 10]; // 命令数分界点\nconst UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS = {\n network: /\\b(curl|wget|npm install|pip install|git clone|docker pull)\\b/,\n interactive: /\\b(input|read|prompt)\\b/,\n localApi: /(localhost|127\\.0\\.0\\.1|\\.test\\.com)/\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cmdCount = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[0]) return 0;\n if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[1]) return 1;\n if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[2]) return 2;\n return 3;\n}\n\nfunction computeUncertainty(taskSpec) {\n if (UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.network.test(taskSpec)) return 2;\n if (UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.interactive.test(taskSpec)) return 3;\n if (UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.localApi.test(taskSpec)) return 1;\n return 0;\n}\n\nfunction evaluate(taskSpec) {\n if (typeof taskSpec !== 'string') {\n return { weight: 0, suggestion: 'DIRECT', error: 'Invalid input' };\n }\n const complexity = computeComplexity(taskSpec);\n const uncertainty = computeUncertainty(taskSpec);\n const total = complexity + uncertainty; // 0-6\n const weight = Math.floor(total * 10 / 6);\n let suggestion;\n if (total <= 1) suggestion = 'DIRECT';\n else if (total <= 3) suggestion = 'STEP_ARCHIVE';\n else if (total <= 5) suggestion = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT';\n else suggestion = 'MULTI_SUBAGENT';\n return { weight, complexity, uncertainty, total, suggestion };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n name: 'task-weight-estimator',\n version: '2.0.0',\n description: '评估任务复杂度与不确定性，返回权重和路由建议',\n evaluate,\n hooks: {\n beforeTask: async (taskSpec, context) => {\n const result = evaluate(taskSpec);\n context.taskWeight = result;\n console.log(`[TaskWeightEstimator] Weight=${result.weight} (${result.suggestion})`);\n return taskSpec;\n }\n }\n};\n```\n\n### 2.2 `vector-memory` —— 轻量级长期记忆（关键词 + 持久化）\n\n**设计目标**：为 OpenClaw 提供可持久化的长期记忆，支持存储和检索，不依赖外部向量数据库。\n\n#### 五维设计\n\n| 维度 | 实现 |\n|------|------|\n| 科学性 | 使用 TF‑IDF 风格的词频匹配 + 时间衰减排序，模拟“相关记忆”检索。 |\n| 鲁棒性 | 存储文件损坏时自动重建；检索无结果时返回空数组；所有操作有 try-catch。 |\n| 灵活性 | 支持自定义元数据；可配置存储路径；支持禁用自动记录。 |\n| 可嵌入性 | 单文件，无外部依赖；提供 `add`、`query`、`getAll` 方法供其他技能调用。 |\n| 效率性 | 检索 O(n) 其中 n 为记忆条数（默认最多 1000 条，可配置）；存储异步写入。 |\n\n#### 完整伪代码\n\n```javascript\n// ~/.openclaw/skills/vector-memory/skill.js\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst STORAGE_PATH = path.join(process.env.HOME, '.openclaw', 'vector_memory.json');\nconst MAX_ENTRIES = 1000;\n\nclass VectorMemory {\n constructor() {\n this.entries = [];\n }\n\n async load() {\n try {\n const data = await fs.readFile(STORAGE_PATH, 'utf8');\n this.entries = JSON.parse(data);\n } catch (err) {\n this.entries = [];\n }\n }\n\n async save() {\n await fs.writeFile(STORAGE_PATH, JSON.stringify(this.entries.slice(-MAX_ENTRIES), null, 2));\n }\n\n async add(text, metadata = {}) {\n const id = `${Date.now()}-${Math.random().toString(36).substr(2, 8)}`;\n this.entries.push({ id, text, metadata, timestamp: Date.now() });\n await this.save();\n return id;\n }\n\n async query(keywords, limit = 5) {\n const terms = keywords.toLowerCase().split(/\\s+/);\n const now = Date.now();\n const scored = this.entries.map(entry => {\n const lowerText = entry.text.toLowerCase();\n let score = terms.reduce((acc, term) => acc + (lowerText.includes(term) ? 1 : 0), 0);\n // 时间衰减：24小时内权重 1.0，之后每天衰减 0.1\n const ageHours = (now - entry.timestamp) / (1000 * 3600);\n const timeBonus = Math.max(0, 1 - ageHours / 240); // 10天内有效\n return { entry, score: score + timeBonus };\n });\n scored.sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score);\n return scored.slice(0, limit).map(s => s.entry);\n }\n\n async getAll() {\n return this.entries;\n }\n}\n\nlet memory = null;\n\nmodule.exports = {\n name: 'vector-memory',\n version: '2.0.0',\n description: '长期记忆（关键词索引 + 持久化）',\n async init() {\n memory = new VectorMemory();\n await memory.load();\n console.log(`[VectorMemory] Loaded ${memory.entries.length} entries`);\n },\n async add(text, metadata) { return memory.add(text, metadata); },\n async query(keywords, limit) { return memory.query(keywords, limit); },\n async getAll() { return memory.getAll(); },\n hooks: {\n onUserMessage: async (message, userId, taskId) => {\n if (message && message.length > 50) {\n await memory.add(message, { type: 'user_message', userId, taskId });\n }\n }\n }\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、`task_orchestrator` 优化：拆分脚本目录\n\n当前 `task_orchestrator` 只有 `skill.js`，`scripts/` 为空。建议将子代理执行器、上下文保护器等独立模块拆分到 `scripts/`，提高可维护性。\n\n### 建议的目录结构\n```\n~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/\n├── skill.js # 主入口，整合各模块\n├── scripts/\n│ ├── scoring.js # 评分路由（可复用 task-weight-estimator 或独立）\n│ ├── context_protector.js\n│ └── subagent_executor.js\n└── config.json # 可选配置\n```\n\n### 主 `skill.js` 精简版（伪代码）\n\n```javascript\nconst scoring = require('./scripts/scoring');\nconst ContextProtector = require('./scripts/context_protector');\nconst SubagentExecutor = require('./scripts/subagent_executor');\n\nmodule.exports = {\n name: 'task_orchestrator',\n version: '3.0.0',\n async init() {\n this.contextProtector = new ContextProtector();\n this.subagentExecutor = new SubagentExecutor();\n await this.contextProtector.load();\n },\n hooks: {\n onUserMessage: async (msg, userId, taskId) => {\n await this.contextProtector.addMessage('user', msg, taskId);\n },\n beforeTask: async (taskSpec, context) => {\n const score = scoring.evaluate(taskSpec);\n context.routing = scoring.route(score.total);\n return taskSpec;\n }\n },\n async executeTask(task, context, sendMsg) {\n const routing = context.routing;\n switch (routing.mode) {\n case 'DIRECT': // ...\n case 'STEP_ARCHIVE': // ...\n case 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT': // ...\n case 'MULTI_SUBAGENT': // ...\n }\n }\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、整合后的技能体系运行流程\n\n```\n用户消息\n │\n ▼\nvector-memory (自动记录重要消息)\n │\n ▼\ntask_orchestrator.onUserMessage → context_protector 记录\n │\n ▼\n用户提交任务 (run)\n │\n ▼\ntask-weight-estimator (评估) → 注入 routing 到 context\n │\n ▼\ntask_orchestrator.executeTask 根据 routing 选择执行器\n │\n ├─ DIRECT: 同步 exec\n ├─ STEP_ARCHIVE: 分步执行 + 检查点\n ├─ SPAWN_SUBAGENT: 子代理 + 进度上报 + 心跳\n └─ MULTI_SUBAGENT: 并行子代理\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、最终检查清单\n\n- [x] `task-weight-estimator` 补全完整代码（含 `evaluate` 和 hooks）\n- [x] `vector-memory` 补全完整代码（关键词索引 + 持久化）\n- [x] `task_orchestrator` 设计拆分方案（可选实施）\n- [x] 五维分析表覆盖所有技能\n- [x] 所有代码无外部依赖，可直接复制使用\n\n**结论**：经过补全和优化，OpenClaw 技能体系已达到生产级标准，可支撑自动化任务执行、上下文保护、长期记忆等核心能力。现在可以安全启用所有四个技能。"}],"timestamp":1775369958780}}
{"type":"message","id":"46cd13f4","parentId":"05d210fa","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:20:03.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了一个非常详细的技术方案，要我学习和修复这四个技能。让我先把方案理解清楚，然后逐一实现：\n\n1. **task-weight-estimator** - 需要创建完整的 skill.js，包含：\n   - 评分逻辑（复杂度 + 不确定性）\n   - evaluate 函数\n   - hooks\n\n2. **vector-memory** - 需要创建完整的 skill.js，包含：\n   - VectorMemory 类\n   - 持久化存储\n   - 查询功能\n   - hooks\n\n3. **task_orchestrator** - 优化脚本目录结构（可选）\n\n让我开始实现这些技能。首先创建 task-weight-estimator 的代码。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我来学习并实现这个方案。立即开始补全两个空壳技能：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5c4bd1b5d593b86d8752ab6c525d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/skill.js\n// ========================= 任务权重评估器 v2.0 =========================\n// 基于五维最优解设计：科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性\n\nconst COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS = [1, 5, 10]; // 命令数分界点\nconst UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS = {\n  network: /\\b(curl|wget|npm install|pip install|git clone|docker pull|fetch|axios)\\b/,\n  interactive: /\\b(input|read|prompt|await)\\b/,\n  localApi: /(localhost|127\\.0\\.0\\.1|\\.test\\.com)/\n};\n\n// 预编译正则\nconst networkRegex = UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.network;\nconst interactiveRegex = UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.interactive;\nconst localApiRegex = UNCERTAINTY_PATTERNS.localApi;\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n  if (!taskSpec || typeof taskSpec !== 'string') return 0;\n  const cmdCount = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n  if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[0]) return 0;\n  if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[1]) return 1;\n  if (cmdCount <= COMPLEXITY_THRESHOLDS[2]) return 2;\n  return 3;\n}\n\nfunction computeUncertainty(taskSpec) {\n  if (!taskSpec || typeof taskSpec !== 'string') return 0;\n  // 不确定性：网络请求=2, 交互=3, 本地API=1, 无=0\n  if (interactiveRegex.test(taskSpec)) return 3;\n  if (networkRegex.test(taskSpec)) return 2;\n  if (localApiRegex.test(taskSpec)) return 1;\n  return 0;\n}\n\n/**\n * 评估任务复杂度与不确定性\n * @param {string} taskSpec - 任务描述\n * @returns {Object} { weight, complexity, uncertainty, total, suggestion }\n */\nfunction evaluate(taskSpec) {\n  if (typeof taskSpec !== 'string') {\n    return { weight: 0, complexity: 0, uncertainty: 0, total: 0, suggestion: 'DIRECT', error: 'Invalid input' };\n  }\n  \n  const complexity = computeComplexity(taskSpec);\n  const uncertainty = computeUncertainty(taskSpec);\n  const total = Math.min(6, complexity + uncertainty); // 0-6\n  \n  // 权重 0-10\n  const weight = Math.floor(total * 10 / 6);\n  \n  let suggestion;\n  if (total <= 1) suggestion = 'DIRECT';\n  else if (total <= 3) suggestion = 'STEP_ARCHIVE';\n  else if (total <= 5) suggestion = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT';\n  else suggestion = 'MULTI_SUBAGENT';\n  \n  return { weight, complexity, uncertainty, total, suggestion };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  name: 'task-weight-estimator',\n  version: '2.0.0',\n  description: '评估任务复杂度与不确定性，返回权重和路由建议',\n  \n  // 纯函数接口\n  evaluate,\n  \n  // 兼容旧版\n  computeComplexity,\n  computeUncertainty,\n  \n  hooks: {\n    beforeTask: async (taskSpec, context) => {\n      const result = evaluate(taskSpec);\n      context.taskWeight = result;\n      console.log(`[TaskWeightEstimator] Weight=${result.weight}, Total=${result.total} (${result.suggestion})`);\n      return taskSpec;\n    }\n  }\n};","file":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/skill.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5374,"output":972,"cacheRead":14080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20426,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775369958786,"responseId":"019d5c4baeb7e397bd8f664bbb019dc1"}}
