{"type":"message","id":"462657e8","parentId":"e2496ef5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:24:17.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check the newly installed skills. I already listed them, but they're asking me to \"检查\" (check/inspect) them - likely meaning verify they're working properly, not just list them.\n\nLet me do a more thorough check - load each skill and verify they work.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22fef752197e494a9ca54803","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 新技能功能验证 ===\" \n\necho -e \"\\n1. task-weight-estimator:\"\nnode -e \"\nconst t = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/skill.js');\nconsole.log('  版本:', t.version);\nconsole.log('  评估测试:', JSON.stringify(t.evaluate('写一个完整博客系统')));\n\"\n\necho -e \"\\n2. vector-memory:\"\nnode -e \"\nconst v = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory/skill.js');\n(async () => {\n  await v.init();\n  const id = await v.add('测试记忆', {test: true});\n  const r = await v.query('测试');\n  console.log('  版本:', v.version);\n  console.log('  存储/检索:', r.length > 0 ? '✅ 正常' : '❌ 失败');\n})();\n\"\n\necho -e \"\\n3. task_orchestrator 脚本模块:\"\nfor m in scoring context_protector subagent_executor; do\n  node --check /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/scripts/$m.js && echo \"  $m.js: ✅\" || echo \"  $m.js: ❌\"\ndone"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":29217,"output":349,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370252739,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ed48e430-43ec-4d3a-b194-3b0030e2633c"}}
