{"type":"message","id":"e0efbc81","parentId":"6edf10d5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:24:44.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问新安装的技能都有什么用。我应该简要说明这4个新技能的功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 新技能功能说明\n\n| 技能 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **task-weight-estimator** | 任务复杂度评估器 - 自动分析任务难易度，返回0-6评分和执行建议（DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/MULTI_SUBAGENT） |\n| **vector-memory** | 长期记忆库 - 关键词索引+时间衰减排序，自动存储重要对话，支持语义搜索 |\n| **task_orchestrator** | 任务编排器 - 整合评分路由、上下文保护、子代理进度上报的自动化执行框架 |\n| **github-manager** | GitHub 管理器 - 代码审查、自动部署、Changelog 生成、CI/CD 配置 |\n\n**联动流程**：\n```\n用户任务 → task-weight-estimator 评分 → task_orchestrator 按评分执行\n                                     ↓\n                              vector-memory 记录重要内容\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":29791,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775370280967,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8a72ac69-e800-45fb-b40a-a75d22d9b01f"}}
