{"type":"message","id":"04ba20c8","parentId":"4ccd0f7c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:26:22.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了关键信息 - OpenClaw 使用 `loadSkillsFromDir` 来加载技能，技能文件是 `skill.js`。\n\n现在我需要创建一个集成方案。让我查看工作区中现有技能是如何被加载的，以及如何在任务执行流程中嵌入评估和记忆功能。\n\n由于 Gateway 是已经运行的进程，最简单的集成方式是创建一个 wrapper 技能或者修改现有流程。但更实际的做法是：\n\n1. 创建一个 `auto-orchestrator` 技能，作为前置拦截器\n2. 在收到用户消息时，自动：\n   - 调用 task-weight-estimator 评分\n   - 根据评分选择执行方式\n   - 将重要内容存入 vector-memory\n\n让我实现这个方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dde7e6ef2d8d4b8386d80e40","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看技能加载目录\necho \"=== 技能加载目录 ===\"\ngrep -r \"skills/\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/auth-profiles*.js 2>/dev/null | grep -oE '\".*skills\"' | sort -u"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":32725,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370379060,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f74f4b7b-704f-4907-8462-cba91500761c"}}
