{"type":"message","id":"b3af1297","parentId":"5c2080f3","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:26:24.910Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_77b944c8ec5442ef80eeaf55","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Workspace 技能目录 ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/claude-code-codingplan/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/self-improving-agent/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-team-orchestration/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/automation-workflows/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/clawdbot-filesystem/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/github-manager/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-github-assistant/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/proactivity/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/productivity-automation-kit/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory/\n\n=== 技能入口 ===\nimport { CURRENT_SESSION_VERSION, DefaultResourceLoader, SessionManager, SettingsManager, codingTools, createAgentSession, createEditTool, createReadTool, createWriteTool, estimateTokens, formatSkillsForPrompt, generateSummary, loadSkillsFromDir, readTool } from \"@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent\";\nimport chokidar from \"chokidar\";\nimport * as ws from \"ws\";\nimport WebSocket$1 from \"ws\";\nimport { Buffer as Buffer$1 } from \"node:buffer\";\nimport { Category, ClientEvent, MatrixEventEvent, MemoryStore, Preset, SyncAccumulator, createClient } from \"matrix-js-sdk/lib/matrix.js\";\n--\n\t\t\t\tskills: unwrapLoadedSkills(loadSkillsFromDir({\n\t\t\t\t\tdir: baseDir,\n\t\t\t\t\tsource: params.source\n\t\t\t\t})),\n\t\t\t\tsource: params.source,\n\t\t\t\trootDir,\n--\n\t\t\tconst loaded = loadSkillsFromDir({\n\t\t\t\tdir: skillDir,\n\t\t\t\tsource: params.source\n\t\t\t});\n\t\t\tloadedSkills.push(...filterLoadedSkillsInsideRoot({\n\t\t\t\tskills: unwrapLoadedSkills(loaded),"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":22,"aggregated":"=== Workspace 技能目录 ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/claude-code-codingplan/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/self-improving-agent/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-team-orchestration/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/automation-workflows/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/clawdbot-filesystem/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/github-manager/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-github-assistant/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/proactivity/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/productivity-automation-kit/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory/\n\n=== 技能入口 ===\nimport { CURRENT_SESSION_VERSION, DefaultResourceLoader, SessionManager, SettingsManager, codingTools, createAgentSession, createEditTool, createReadTool, createWriteTool, estimateTokens, formatSkillsForPrompt, generateSummary, loadSkillsFromDir, readTool } from \"@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent\";\nimport chokidar from \"chokidar\";\nimport * as ws from \"ws\";\nimport WebSocket$1 from \"ws\";\nimport { Buffer as Buffer$1 } from \"node:buffer\";\nimport { Category, ClientEvent, MatrixEventEvent, MemoryStore, Preset, SyncAccumulator, createClient } from \"matrix-js-sdk/lib/matrix.js\";\n--\n\t\t\t\tskills: unwrapLoadedSkills(loadSkillsFromDir({\n\t\t\t\t\tdir: baseDir,\n\t\t\t\t\tsource: params.source\n\t\t\t\t})),\n\t\t\t\tsource: params.source,\n\t\t\t\trootDir,\n--\n\t\t\tconst loaded = loadSkillsFromDir({\n\t\t\t\tdir: skillDir,\n\t\t\t\tsource: params.source\n\t\t\t});\n\t\t\tloadedSkills.push(...filterLoadedSkillsInsideRoot({\n\t\t\t\tskills: unwrapLoadedSkills(loaded),","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775370384906}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cd4dfb2","parentId":"b3af1297","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:27:11.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了，OpenClaw 会自动扫描 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 和 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 目录下的 `skill.js` 文件。\n\n由于 Gateway 已经在运行，添加新技能后需要重启 Gateway 才能生效。\n\n我有两个集成方案：\n\n**方案 1（轻量）**：创建一个 wrapper/hook 技能，在用户消息时自动：\n1. 调用 task-weight-estimator 评分\n2. 存 vector-memory\n3. 注入评分到 context\n\n**方案 2（完整）**：修改 task_orchestrator 技能，使其成为\"自动编排入口\"，拦截所有任务\n\n考虑到 Gateway 重启需要用户操作，我选择方案 1：创建一个 `auto-orchestrator` 技能作为前置拦截器。\n\n让我创建这个技能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在我来创建一个 **自动编排入口技能**，集成评分和记忆功能：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5c519d0415587e37a1dd8bc7867f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/auto-orchestrator/skill.js\n// ========================= 自动编排入口 v1.0 =========================\n// 自动集成: task-weight-estimator + vector-memory + task_orchestrator\n// 作为前置拦截器，在任务执行前自动评分并记录记忆\n\nconst path = require('path');\n\n// 延迟加载依赖技能\nlet taskWeightEstimator = null;\nlet vectorMemory = null;\nlet scoring = null;\n\nasync function loadDependencies() {\n  if (!taskWeightEstimator) {\n    try {\n      taskWeightEstimator = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-weight-estimator/skill.js');\n      scoring = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/scripts/scoring.js');\n      console.log('[AutoOrchestrator] Loaded task-weight-estimator');\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.error('[AutoOrchestrator] Failed to load dependencies:', e.message);\n    }\n  }\n  if (!vectorMemory) {\n    try {\n      vectorMemory = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory/skill.js');\n      await vectorMemory.init();\n      console.log('[AutoOrchestrator] Loaded vector-memory');\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.error('[AutoOrchestrator] Failed to load vector-memory:', e.message);\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  name: 'auto-orchestrator',\n  version: '1.0.0',\n  description: '自动编排入口 - 任务评分 + 记忆存储 + 执行路由',\n\n  async init() {\n    await loadDependencies();\n    console.log('[AutoOrchestrator] Initialized - 任务评分和记忆功能已启用');\n  },\n\n  hooks: {\n    // 用户消息前置拦截：评分 + 记录记忆\n    onUserMessage: async (message, userId, taskId) => {\n      await loadDependencies();\n      \n      // 1. 自动记录重要消息到 vector-memory\n      if (vectorMemory && message && message.length > 30) {\n        try {\n          // 跳过包含 skill.js 或 hook 的内部消息\n          if (!message.includes('【') && !message.includes('hook')) {\n            await vectorMemory.add(message, { type: 'user_message', userId, taskId });\n          }\n        } catch (e) {\n          // 静默失败，不影响主流程\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // 返回原消息，不做任何修改\n      return message;\n    },\n\n    // 任务执行前评分\n    beforeTask: async (taskSpec, context) => {\n      await loadDependencies();\n      \n      // 调用 task-weight-estimator 评分\n      if (taskWeightEstimator && taskSpec) {\n        const result = taskWeightEstimator.evaluate(taskSpec);\n        context.taskWeight = result;\n        \n        // 同时也计算路由\n        if (scoring) {\n          const route = scoring.route(result);\n          context.taskRoute = route;\n        }\n        \n        console.log(`[AutoOrchestrator] 任务评分: total=${result.total}, suggestion=${result.suggestion}`);\n      }\n      \n      return taskSpec;\n    },\n\n    // 任务完成后记录\n    afterTask: async (result, context) => {\n      await loadDependencies();\n      \n      // 存储任务结果到记忆\n      if (vectorMemory && result && typeof result === 'string' && result.length > 50) {\n        try {\n          await vectorMemory.add(result, { \n            type: 'task_result', \n            taskWeight: context.taskWeight?.total \n          });\n        } catch (e) {\n          // 静默失败\n        }\n      }\n      \n      return result;\n    }\n  },\n\n  // 供其他技能调用的 API\n  api: {\n    // 评分\n    evaluate: (taskSpec) => taskWeightEstimator?.evaluate(taskSpec),\n    \n    // 路由建议\n    getRoute: (taskSpec) => {\n      if (!taskWeightEstimator || !scoring) return null;\n      const score = taskWeightEstimator.evaluate(taskSpec);\n      return scoring.route(score);\n    },\n    \n    // 记忆查询\n    searchMemory: (keywords) => vectorMemory?.query(keywords),\n    \n    // 存储记忆\n    remember: (text, metadata) => vectorMemory?.add(text, metadata)\n  }\n};","file":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/auto-orchestrator/skill.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2544,"output":1119,"cacheRead":31104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370384911,"responseId":"019d5c5177f41cb8776e1c6a6a2433c1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9687f985","parentId":"3cd4dfb2","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:27:11.903Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5c519d0415587e37a1dd8bc7867f","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 3480 bytes to ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/auto-orchestrator/skill.js"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775370431896}}
{"type":"message","id":"39c6391e","parentId":"9687f985","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:27:22.537Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建 SKILL.md 文件，然后验证语法并重启 Gateway 使技能生效。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d73017bf767e4e70a13ebdb0","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: auto-orchestrator\ndescription: 自动编排入口技能 - 自动集成任务评分、记忆存储、执行路由。为每次任务自动评估复杂度，存储重要对话到长期记忆，根据评分选择最佳执行模式。\n---\n\n# Auto Orchestrator - 自动编排入口\n\n## 功能\n\n### 1. 任务自动评分\n- 在 `beforeTask` hook 中自动调用 `task-weight-estimator`\n- 评估结果注入 `context.taskWeight`\n- 同时计算路由建议 `context.taskRoute`\n\n### 2. 记忆自动存储\n- 在 `onUserMessage` hook 中自动记录用户消息（长度>30字符）\n- 在 `afterTask` hook 中自动记录任务结果\n- 支持语义搜索 `api.searchMemory(keywords)`\n\n### 3. 执行模式路由\n根据评分自动选择执行模式：\n- 0-1分: DIRECT（直接执行）\n- 2-3分: STEP_ARCHIVE（分步执行）\n- 4-5分: SPAWN_SUBAGENT（子代理）\n- 6分: MULTI_SUBAGENT（并行子代理）\n\n## 使用方式\n\n技能自动启用，无需手动调用。\n\n手动调用 API：\n```javascript\nconst orchestrator = require('./skill.js');\n\n// 评分\nconst score = orchestrator.api.evaluate('写一个博客系统');\n\n// 路由\nconst route = orchestrator.api.getRoute('写一个博客系统');\n\n// 搜索记忆\nconst memories = await orchestrator.api.searchMemory('博客');\n\n// 存储记忆\nawait orchestrator.api.remember('用户偏好深色主题', { type: 'preference' });\n```\n\n## 依赖\n\n- task-weight-estimator\n- task_orchestrator/scripts/scoring.js\n- vector-memory\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n用户消息 → auto-orchestrator.onUserMessage → 存储到 vector-memory\n     ↓\n任务执行 → auto-orchestrator.beforeTask → task-weight-estimator 评分 → 注入 context\n     ↓\n任务完成 → auto-orchestrator.afterTask → 存储结果到 vector-memory\n```","file":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/auto-orchestrator/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":34770,"output":485,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370431903,"responseId":"chatcmpl-def5ac08-4155-492e-a225-91b501726238"}}
