{"type":"message","id":"ef2b1b9c","parentId":"1f571a8b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:34:17.639Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_56ed08f55d684067b6bee990","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — I'm not saying your workflow is chaotic... I'm just bringing a linter and a helmet.\n\nUsage: openclaw hooks [options] [command]\n\nManage internal agent hooks\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check hooks eligibility status\n  disable     Disable a hook\n  enable      Enable a hook\n  info        Show detailed information about a hook\n  install     Deprecated: install a hook pack via `openclaw plugins install`\n  list        List all hooks\n  update      Deprecated: update hook packs via `openclaw plugins update`\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/hooks"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2101,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — I'm not saying your workflow is chaotic... I'm just bringing a linter and a helmet.\n\nUsage: openclaw hooks [options] [command]\n\nManage internal agent hooks\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check hooks eligibility status\n  disable     Disable a hook\n  enable      Enable a hook\n  info        Show detailed information about a hook\n  install     Deprecated: install a hook pack via `openclaw plugins install`\n  list        List all hooks\n  update      Deprecated: update hook packs via `openclaw plugins update`\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/hooks","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775370857635}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f88b3ee","parentId":"ef2b1b9c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:34:32.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 hooks 是内置的，不容易添加自定义 hook。让我看看有没有其他方式。\n\n一个更直接的解决方案是：在我的响应流程中直接嵌入评分逻辑。也就是说，每次收到用户消息，如果这是一个任务，我立即显示评分结果。\n\n让我创建一个更实用的解决方案：在 workspace 中创建一个自动执行的脚本，每次会话开始时加载。不过，这可能需要修改 BOOTSTRAP.md 或类似机制。\n\n让我换一个角度：我直接在当前响应流程中执行评分，并通过输出告诉用户评分结果。这就是所谓的\"知行合一\" - 说到做到。\n\n总结一下我目前做的：\n1. 创建了 task-weight-estimator 技能（已测试通过）\n2. 创建了 auto-orchestrator 技能（代码已完成）\n3. 创建了前置评分脚本 run_first.js（已测试通过）\n\n问题是：如何让 Gateway 自动加载这些技能？\n\n可能的解决方案：\n1. 使用 skills 命令查看当前加载的技能\n2. 修改 config 让某些技能默认启用\n3. 直接在响应中嵌入评分（不需要 Gateway 层面的集成）\n\n让我先检查 skills 命令看看有没有办法。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5c58f9a04f854e02b9193389a602","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看 skills 命令\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw skills 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7956,"output":265,"cacheRead":38784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370857640,"responseId":"019d5c58c69be6a5ab5522c5f3fd3934"}}
