{"type":"message","id":"e1b3075d","parentId":"4ef2c58e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:34:47.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太棒了！Gateway 已经加载了：\n- ✅ auto-orchestrator (ready)- ✅ task-weight-estimator (ready)\n\n这说明技能已经被 Gateway 识别和加载了！现在的问题是它们是否在执行流程中真正起作用。\n\n让我验证一下这些技能是否真的在工作流程中被调用。我可以通过查看日志或者实际触发一个任务来测试。\n\n让我先总结一下当前的状态，告诉用户：技能已经被加载了，现在需要验证它们是否真的在执行流程中起作用。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50964b4916774d84b8cb7356","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 验证技能是否真正在工作\necho \"=== 验证技能 Hooks 是否被调用 ===\"\n\n# 发送一个测试任务消息，通过 API 模拟\n# 查看是否有日志记录\n\n# 检查 vector-memory 是否有新的记录\necho \"记忆存储记录:\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/vector_memory.json 2>/dev/null | grep -c \"id\" && echo \"条\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 总结当前状态 ===\"\necho \"✅ task-weight-estimator: 已加载\"\necho \"✅ auto-orchestrator: 已加载\"\necho \"✅ vector-memory: 3 条记录\"\n\necho -e \"\\n⚠️ 但需要验证 hooks 是否真正触发\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":47993,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775370882967,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ad17c461-551c-4916-8652-c6de179943ae"}}
