{"type":"message","id":"6b9fbd2b","parentId":"47f6d4ae","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:37:44.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求全自动 - 即我收到任务后，系统自动完成评分、路由、执行，不需要手动。\n\n现在的问题是：\n1. 我有代码（auto-orchestrator, task-weight-estimator）\n2. 代码已经被 Gateway 加载（skills list 显示 ready）\n3. 但 hooks 没有真正触发\n\n需要想办法让 hooks 自动触发。有几个思路：\n1. 检查 Gateway 的 hooks 是否能添加自定义 skill hooks\n2. 重启 Gateway 强制重新加载所有技能和 hooks\n3. 找到 skill hooks 触发的机制\n\n让我查看一下 Gateway 日志或者 hooks 机制。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5c5be1086161cd78051fb9ddc96f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看 Gateway 是否有关于 skill hooks 的日志\necho \"=== 查找 hooks 触发机制 ===\"\n\n# 查看 hooks-cli 的功能\ngrep -r \"hook\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/*.js 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"skill\\|onUser\\|beforeTask\" | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 尝试重启 Gateway 让 hooks 真正生效 ===\"\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}' | xargs kill 2>/dev/null\nsleep 2\n\n# 使用正确的方式启动 Gateway\ncd ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist\nnohup node gateway.js > ~/.openclaw/gateway.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 3\n\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | head -1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":9538,"output":336,"cacheRead":40320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775371044803,"responseId":"019d5c5bbccf648d493824c19726fc9b"}}
