{"type":"message","id":"43f556d8","parentId":"1bcc108b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:46:40.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 正常运行，技能也加载了。让我向用户报告状态。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 集成完成\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **Gateway** | ✅ 运行中 (PID 5396) |\n| **auto-orchestrator** | ✅ 已加载 v1.1 |\n| **task-weight-estimator** | ✅ 已加载 |\n| **context_server** | ✅ 在线 (端口 18790) |\n| **本地评分** | ✅ 双评分机制 |\n| **保护层评分** | ✅ 4维 + 负载降级 |\n\n**现在的全自动流程**：\n```\n用户消息 → auto-orchestrator.onUserMessage \n         → 记录到 vector-memory + 上报到 context_server\n              ↓\n任务执行 → auto-orchestrator.beforeTask \n         → 本地评分 (task-weight-estimator)\n         → 保护层评分 (task_scorer 4维)\n         → 取较保守的超时时间\n              ↓\n任务完成 → auto-orchestrator.afterTask\n         → 存储结果到记忆 + 上报保护层\n```\n\n现在应该真正实现全自动了 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4309,"output":235,"cacheRead":56960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61504,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775371586164,"responseId":"019d5c6400a7449c83e2c7a4124967c5"}}
