{"type":"message","id":"69c8d726","parentId":"591ede00","timestamp":"2026-04-05T07:14:29.704Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5c7d6d717c34556e8663ec7fcf6d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 已完成的 v7.0 模块 ===\n\n1. scoring.js 功能:\n * 核心模块：评分因子 + 路由决策 + 上下文保护\n * 八大核心模块:\n * 6. 安全模块 - 命令白名单动态管理、路径沙箱、敏感信息脱敏\n// ============ 模块1: 评分因子垂直拓展 =============\nclass TaskScorerV7 {\n\n2. 代码行数:\n356 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"=== 已完成的 v7.0 模块 ===\n\n1. scoring.js 功能:\n * 核心模块：评分因子 + 路由决策 + 上下文保护\n * 八大核心模块:\n * 6. 安全模块 - 命令白名单动态管理、路径沙箱、敏感信息脱敏\n// ============ 模块1: 评分因子垂直拓展 =============\nclass TaskScorerV7 {\n\n2. 代码行数:\n356 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775373269700}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c12f597","parentId":"69c8d726","timestamp":"2026-04-05T07:14:33.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"子代理完成了评分因子模块，但任务超时了。让我向用户汇报这个进度，并询问是否要继续。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ⚠️ 子代理任务超时\n\n子代理运行了约 5 分钟，完成了部分工作：\n\n| 模块 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **评分因子** | ✅ 完成 (356行代码) |\n| 路由决策 | ❌ 未完成 |\n| 上下文保护 | ❌ 未完成 |\n| 超大任务执行器 | ❌ 未完成 |\n| 其他模块 | ❌ 未完成 |\n\n**已完成的功能**（scoring.js）：\n- 多源输入适配（taskSpec/文本/消息数组）\n- 6维评分因子：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n- 权重自适应学习\n- 评分结果缓存\n\n要继续完成剩余模块吗？可以：\n1. 继续spawn一个子代理完成\n2. 我直接在这里继续实现 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":78661,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78857,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775373269706,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3e0abcd4-c080-4df0-91d2-1c81ebee148c"}}
