{"type":"message","id":"bb740865","parentId":"f4477313","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:06:54.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I actually followed this rule - did I do the scoring before executing? Let me check what just happened in this conversation.\n\nLooking at the recent exchanges:\n1. User asked \"你执行什么才会进行评分\" (What triggers scoring?)\n2. I explained the scoring rules\n3. Now user is asking \"执行了吗\" (Did you execute it?)\n\nThe user is pointing out that when they asked me to explain the scoring rules, I just explained it without actually triggering a scoring first. I should have said:\n\n\"📊 评分: X/Y (Z模式) - 解释规则\"\n→ 然后再解释\n\nBut I just started explaining the rules directly. This is another case of not following my own rules - I should score first, then act.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对，我刚刚又犯错了。\n\n你问我\"执行什么才会进行评分\"，我应该：\n\n```\n📊 评分: 0/6 (DIRECT) - 简单查询任务\n↓\n然后解释评分规则\n```\n\n但我直接就开始解释，**没有先评分**。\n\n**问题根源**：只有通过 **HTTP API (/api/task)** 调用 Router 时才会自动评分。我直接回答问题时走的是**内部对话**，没有触发评分流程。\n\n**解决方案**：我需要在每次回答前都手动调用评分，或者把评分集成到对话流程中。\n\n要修复吗？以后每次对话我都会先显示评分 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":121934,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775376409380,"responseId":"chatcmpl-78896ee2-ca8a-488c-ac04-fcc3e75e4b00"}}
