{"type":"message","id":"15ff7379","parentId":"4c0dc9aa","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:16:50.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"context_server 显示 messageCount: 0，说明没有记录任何消息。虽然 openclaw-router.js 中有调用 contextProtector.addMessage，但看起来没有被触发，或者只是在 API 调用时工作，不是自动在每次对话中工作。让我解释给用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**当前状态**：context_server 显示 messageCount: 0，**没有自动工作**。\n\n**原因**：\n- `contextProtector.addMessage` 只在 **Router API (/api/task)** 被调用时才会记录\n- 我的**对话回答**没有触发这个记录\n\n**要实现自动工作**，需要：\n1. 在每次对话时主动调用 contextProtector\n2. 或者通过 Gateway 的 hooks 触发\n\n目前只有：\n- HTTP API 调用 → 会记录\n- 对话回答 → 不记录\n\n要让它自动工作吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":877,"output":165,"cacheRead":125056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126098,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775376994196,"responseId":"019d5cb70b9600e036b49a5e2ac6edd3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f45b8494","parentId":"15ff7379","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:29:33.903Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 16:29 GMT+8] 先分析，回答我：希望使用 **独立 Context API + 反向代理拦截对话请求** 的方案（不修改 OpenClaw 源码），下面给出一个**增强、强壮、可直接运行**的 `openclaw-router.js`，它能够：\n\n1. **拦截用户消息**（通过配置的对话路径，如 `/api/chat/send`, `/webhook` 等）。\n2. **拦截 AI 回复**（通过代理的 `onProxyRes` 钩子，解析响应体中的 AI 消息）。\n3. **异步非阻塞**记录到独立 Context API，不影响正常请求。\n4. **处理流式响应**（SSE）和 JSON 响应两种格式。\n5. **鲁棒性增强**：超时、错误静默、健康检查、代理重试。\n\n---\n\n## 最终版 `openclaw-router.js`（完整代码）\n\n```javascript\n// openclaw-router.js\n// 反向代理 + 自动记录对话（用户消息 + AI 回复）到独立 Context API\n\nconst express = require('express');\nconst { createProxyMiddleware } = require('http-proxy-middleware');\nconst axios = require('axios');\nconst { Readable } = require('stream');\n\n// ========== 配置（环境变量） ==========\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.OPENCLAW_GATEWAY || 'http://localhost:3000';\nconst ROUTER_PORT = parseInt(process.env.ROUTER_PORT || '3002', 10);\nconst CONTEXT_API_URL = process.env.CONTEXT_API_URL || 'http://localhost:3001/api/context';\nconst CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS = parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000', 10);\nconst ENABLE_CONTEXT = process.env.ENABLE_CONTEXT !== 'false';\n\n// 对话请求路径（支持多个）\nconst CONVERSATION_PATHS = [\n '/api/chat/send',\n '/api/message',\n '/webhook',\n '/v1/chat/completions'\n];\n\n// 消息字段候选（按优先级）\nconst MESSAGE_FIELDS = ['message', 'text', 'content', 'prompt', 'input'];\n\n// ========== 辅助函数 ==========\nfunction extractMessage(body) {\n if (!body) return null;\n for (const field of MESSAGE_FIELDS) {\n if (typeof body[field] === 'string' && body[field].trim()) {\n return body[field].trim();\n }\n }\n // 处理 { messages: [{ role, content }] } 格式\n if (body.messages && Array.isArray(body.messages)) {\n const last = body.messages[body.messages.length - 1];\n if (last && last.content) return last.content;\n }\n return null;\n}\n\nasync function recordContext(role, content, conversationId = null) {\n if (!ENABLE_CONTEXT || !content) return;\n try {\n await axios.post(CONTEXT_API_URL, {\n role,\n content,\n conversationId,\n timestamp: Date.now()\n }, { timeout: CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS });\n } catch (err) {\n // 静默失败，仅打印日志\n console.error(`[Context] Failed to record ${role} message:`, err.message);\n }\n}\n\n// 从响应体中提取 AI 回复（支持 JSON 和 SSE 流）\nfunction extractAssistantMessage(body, contentType) {\n if (contentType && contentType.includes('text/event-stream')) {\n // SSE 流：每行 data: {...}，取最后一条非 [DONE]\n const lines = body.split('\\n');\n let lastData = null;\n for (const line of lines) {\n if (line.startsWith('data: ')) {\n const jsonStr = line.slice(6);\n if (jsonStr !== '[DONE]') {\n try {\n lastData = JSON.parse(jsonStr);\n } catch (e) {}\n }\n }\n }\n if (lastData) {\n return lastData.choices?.[0]?.delta?.content || lastData.content || null;\n }\n return null;\n } else {\n // JSON 响应\n try {\n const json = JSON.parse(body);\n if (json.choices && json.choices[0]) {\n return json.choices[0].message?.content || json.choices[0].text;\n }\n return json.reply || json.response || json.content || null;\n } catch (e) {\n // 非 JSON，返回纯文本（可能为空）\n return body.trim() || null;\n }\n }\n}\n\n// ========== Express 应用 ==========\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json({ limit: '10mb' }));\napp.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: true }));\n\n// 健康检查\napp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n res.json({\n status: 'ok',\n uptime: process.uptime(),\n gateway: GATEWAY_URL,\n contextApi: CONTEXT_API_URL\n });\n});\n\n// 拦截用户消息请求\nfor (const pathPattern of CONVERSATION_PATHS) {\n app.post(pathPattern, async (req, res, next) => {\n const userMessage = extractMessage(req.body);\n if (userMessage) {\n const convId = req.body.conversationId || req.body.sessionId || req.body.chatId || null;\n await recordContext('user', userMessage, convId);\n }\n next();\n });\n}\n\n// 创建代理（带响应拦截）\nconst proxyMiddleware = createProxyMiddleware({\n target: GATEWAY_URL,\n changeOrigin: true,\n // 启用响应拦截\n selfHandleResponse: true,\n onProxyRes: async (proxyRes, req, res) => {\n // 收集响应体\n const chunks = [];\n proxyRes.on('data', chunk => chunks.push(chunk));\n proxyRes.on('end', async () => {\n const body = Buffer.concat(chunks).toString('utf8');\n const contentType = proxyRes.headers['content-type'] || '';\n const assistantMsg = extractAssistantMessage(body, contentType);\n if (assistantMsg) {\n const convId = req.body?.conversationId || req.body?.sessionId || null;\n await recordContext('assistant', assistantMsg, convId);\n }\n // 将原始响应发送给客户端\n res.writeHead(proxyRes.statusCode, proxyRes.headers);\n res.end(body);\n });\n proxyRes.on('error', (err) => {\n console.error('[Proxy] Response stream error:', err.message);\n if (!res.headersSent) res.status(502).end();\n });\n },\n onError: (err, req, res) => {\n console.error('[Proxy] Error:', err.message);\n if (!res.headersSent) res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unreachable' });\n }\n});\n\napp.use('/', proxyMiddleware);\n\n// 启动服务\napp.listen(ROUTER_PORT, () => {\n console.log(`[Router] Listening on port ${ROUTER_PORT}`);\n console.log(`[Router] Forwarding to Gateway: ${GATEWAY_URL}`);\n console.log(`[Router] Context API: ${CONTEXT_API_URL}`);\n console.log(`[Router] Conversation paths: ${CONVERSATION_PATHS.join(', ')}`);\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 配套 `context-api.js`（独立服务，与之前相同）\n\n确保该服务运行在 `http://localhost:3001`。\n\n---\n\n## 部署与验证\n\n1. **启动 Context API**：\n ```bash\n node context-api.js\n # 应输出：Context API on 3001\n ```\n\n2. **启动反向代理中间件**：\n ```bash\n node openclaw-router.js\n # 应输出：Router listening on port 3002 ...\n ```\n\n3. **配置 OpenClaw Gateway 的地址**： \n 将原来直接访问 Gateway 的客户端（如 OpenClaw 前端、CLI）改为访问 `http://localhost:3002`（中间件地址）。例如，如果原来调用 `http://localhost:3000/api/chat/send`，现在改为 `http://localhost:3002/api/chat/send`。\n\n4. **测试对话**：\n - 发送一条消息（例如 `Hello`）到中间件的对话接口。\n - 查看 Context API 状态：\n ```bash\n curl http://localhost:3001/api/context/status\n ```\n 应看到 `messages` 计数增加（用户消息 + AI 回复两条）。\n\n5. **测试自动压缩**：连续发送 50 条消息，观察 Context API 日志是否输出 `Summarized ...`。\n\n---\n\n## 鲁棒性特性\n\n- **异步记录**：不阻塞请求/响应，超时 2 秒。\n- **错误静默**：Context API 不可用时，仅打印错误，不影响正常对话。\n- **健康检查**：`/health` 可监控。\n- **响应体缓冲**：对于小型 JSON 响应，缓冲后解析；对于大型流式响应（SSE），仍能提取最后一条消息。\n- **代理错误处理**：Gateway 不可达时返回 502。\n\n---\n\n现在，您的系统已经能够**自动记录所有对话（用户+AI）**，当消息数或字符数达到阈值时，Context API 会自动压缩并写入长期记忆，彻底解决上下文撑爆问题。\n\n如果您在测试中遇到任何问题（如响应体解析失败、路径不匹配等），请提供具体的请求/响应示例，我可以进一步调整正则和提取逻辑。"}],"timestamp":1775377773890}}
