{"type":"message","id":"ab8d2d80","parentId":"c1597abe","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:30:02.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我分析用户提供的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n📊 评分: 1.6/6 (DIRECT)\n\n---\n\n## 方案分析\n\n用户提供的方案是：**独立 Context API + 反向代理拦截对话请求**\n\n### 方案原理\n\n```\n用户 → Router (3002) → Gateway (3000)\n         ↓\n    拦截用户消息 → 异步记录到 Context API (3001)\n         ↓\n    拦截 AI 回复 → 异步记录到 Context API (3001)\n```\n\n### 优点\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **不修改源码** | 通过反向代理实现 |\n| **异步非阻塞** | 记录不影响响应时间 |\n| **支持流式响应** | SSE 也能提取 AI 回复 |\n| **鲁棒性** | 超时、错误静默 |\n\n### 当前问题\n\n我们现有的 `openclaw-router.js` **只记录了 HTTP API 调用**，没有记录对话（Chat）请求。\n\n### 需要补充\n\n1. 增加对话路径拦截：\n   - `/api/chat/send`\n   - `/api/message`\n   - `/webhook`\n\n2. 代理网关请求，拦截响应\n\n---\n\n等待确认是否按这个方案实现？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":127812,"output":252,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775377777519,"responseId":"019d5cc25f447b4944600117d94a39b0"}}
