{"type":"message","id":"a75627ba","parentId":"bd2dd29e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:39:33.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我整理一下今天写的技能：\n\n今天创建的技能（2026-04-05）：\n\n1. task-orchestrator-v7 - 全自动任务编排系统，包含：\n   - scoring.js - 6维评分\n   - mega_executor.js - 分片并行执行\n   - context_protector.js - 上下文保护\n   - progress_reporter.js - 进度上报\n   - security.js - 安全模块\n   - optimizer.js - 效率优化\n   - openclaw-router.js - 反向代理中间件\n   - quick_score.js - 快速评分函数\n\n之前创建但已删除的：\n- task-weight-estimator\n- vector-memory\n- task_orchestrator\n- auto-orchestrator\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n今天创建的 **task-orchestrator-v7** 技能：\n\n| 文件 | 功能 | 行数 |\n|------|------|------|\n| scoring.js | 6维评分（logic/risk/duration/resource/uncertainty/dependency） | 356 |\n| mega_executor.js | 分片并行执行、超大任务 | 159 |\n| context_protector.js | 上下文保护、token计数 | 238 |\n| progress_reporter.js | 进度上报、自适应心跳 | 426 |\n| security.js | 白名单、沙箱、脱敏 | 154 |\n| optimizer.js | LRU缓存、健康检查 | 148 |\n| openclaw-router.js | 反向代理、对话拦截 | 425 |\n| quick_score.js | 快速评分 | 27 |\n\n**共 8 个模块，~2000 行代码**。\n\n之前删除的：task-weight-estimator、vector-memory、task_orchestrator、auto-orchestrator 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":135661,"output":347,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378365599,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b7f98acd-4d8c-4a9d-8460-b570de49e9b7"}}
