{"type":"message","id":"4b0e6120","parentId":"02c2ff53","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:40:29.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问这些技能有什么用。我需要简洁地解释 task-orchestrator-v7 的用途。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**task-orchestrator-v7** 的作用：\n\n```\n用户任务 → Router (3002)\n           ↓\n        评分 (scoring.js)\n           ↓\n        路由决策 (DIRECT/PARALLEL/MEGA)\n           ↓\n        执行 (mega_executor.js) / 转发 Gateway\n           ↓\n        记录上下文 (context_server:18790)\n```\n\n**核心功能**：\n| 模块 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| scoring | 自动评估任务复杂度，决定怎么执行 |\n| mega_executor | 大任务自动分片并行（多核利用） |\n| context_protector | 保护上下文，防止撑爆 |\n| security | 命令白名单、敏感信息脱敏 |\n| optimizer | 结果缓存、健康检查 |\n| openclaw-router | 反向代理，拦截对话自动记录上下文 |\n| quick_score | 每次对话前快速评分 |\n\n**一句话**：\n自动评估任务复杂度 → 选择最佳执行方式 → 保护对话上下文\n\n🇴"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":769,"output":223,"cacheRead":134912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378413951,"responseId":"019d5cccb62a5706f45a16bc536973af"}}
