{"type":"message","id":"44f99df8","parentId":"5bac2afd","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:46:59.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 使用 WebSocket 进行通信！这是为什么我们的 HTTP 拦截无法捕获 AI 回复的原因。让我告诉用户这个发现，并询问是否需要实现 WebSocket 拦截（这更复杂）。或者，目前的实现已经可以工作：- HTTP API 调用（如 /api/task）→ 正常记录- WebSocket 对话 → 需要特殊处理\n\n让我告诉用户当前状态。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**发现问题**：Gateway 使用 **WebSocket** 而非 HTTP REST API 来处理对话！\n\n```\nWebSocket 连接: ✅ 成功\nHTTP POST 对话: ❌ 404\n```\n\n**当前状态**：\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 用户消息 (HTTP) | ✅ 已记录 |\n| AI 回复 (HTTP) | ❌ 无法捕获 |\n| WebSocket 对话 | ⚠️ 需要额外实现 |\n\n**解决方案**：\n1. **简单方案**：保持现状，HTTP 请求可以拦截，WebSocket 目前无法拦截\n2. **复杂方案**：实现 WebSocket 代理拦截（需要升级依赖）\n\n要继续实现 WebSocket 拦截吗？还是先保持现状？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3403,"output":222,"cacheRead":136832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378796268,"responseId":"019d5cd2838cc6cd41bce7bb6a6642de"}}
