{"type":"message","id":"1f7b5aef","parentId":"b595ea11","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:48:55.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我能不能做到：输出之前先评分，再等待确认。\n\n这和之前的规则类似，但是更严格 - 不仅仅是执行任务评分，而是每次\"输出\"（回答）都要先评分。\n\n让我重新理解：\n- 用户发来消息\n- 我在回答之前，先进行评分\n- 等待用户确认后，再输出回答\n\n这和\"任务执行评分确认\"类似，但是是针对所有对话回复。\n\n让我测试一下这个流程：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1bb6b977663e41ceb5d98adc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node --input-type=module -e \"\nimport('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/quick_score.js').then(m => {\n  const r = m.default('你能不能做到输出之前先评分，再等待确认');\n  console.log('📊 评分:', r.total, '/6 (', r.suggestion, ')');\n});\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":140336,"output":192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140528,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775378930696,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2207d5a6-1a84-4e34-b3ee-d81260f42d54"}}
