{"type":"message","id":"20d498f4","parentId":"b7cb0df8","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:49:05.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是关于\"回复前评分\"的规则。让我分析并回答。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n📊 评分: 1.6/6 (DIRECT)\n\n**可以做到**。流程：\n\n```\n用户消息\n  ↓\n我进行评分（判断是否需要详细回答）\n  ↓\n等待你确认\n  ↓\n我输出回答\n```\n\n但这和之前\"评分→执行→等待确认\"的区别是：\n- 之前：针对**任务执行**\n- 现在：针对**所有回复**\n\n当前规则是：**任务执行**需要评分确认。\n\n你是希望扩展到**所有回复**都先评分确认吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1682,"output":130,"cacheRead":138752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140564,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775378935634,"responseId":"019d5cd3f55d83667720d65a7ab0654b"}}
