{"type":"message","id":"84a50c03","parentId":"30a56e18","timestamp":"2026-04-05T09:19:53.162Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 17:19 GMT+8] 分析一下：# 自动化项目改进系统（自主迭代，无需人工确认）最优解 v1.0\n\n> 用户只需提供**最终目标**（例如“重构 `src/` 目录，使代码符合 ESLint 标准且所有测试通过”），系统自动执行多轮分析、计划、修改、评估，直到目标达成或达到最大迭代次数。 \n> **五维设计**：科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性。 \n> **无需人工干预**：完全自主运行。\n\n---\n\n## 一、系统架构\n\n```\n用户目标 → 项目快照 → 迭代循环\n │\n ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐\n │ │ │\n 分析模块 计划模块 执行模块\n (评估当前状态) (生成改进动作) (应用修改+测试)\n │ │ │\n └───────────────┼───────────────┘\n │\n 评估模块\n (检查目标达成度)\n │\n 未达成 → 继续迭代（最多 N 次）\n 达成 → 输出最终结果\n```\n\n所有模块均为无状态函数，通过共享工作区（项目路径）和检查点文件持久化状态。\n\n---\n\n## 二、核心模块设计与伪代码\n\n### 2.1 目标解析与量化指标\n\n将自然语言目标转化为可评估的检查项和阈值。\n\n```javascript\n// goalParser.js\nfunction parseGoal(goalText) {\n // 预定义规则（可扩展）\n const rules = [\n { pattern: /ESLint|代码规范/i, metric: 'eslint', threshold: 0, comparator: '==' },\n { pattern: /测试通过/i, metric: 'test_pass_rate', threshold: 1.0, comparator: '>=' },\n { pattern: /圈复杂度.*\\d+/, metric: 'complexity', threshold: 5, comparator: '<=' },\n { pattern: /性能提升|更快/i, metric: 'performance', threshold: 20, comparator: 'improve_percent' }\n ];\n const metrics = [];\n for (const rule of rules) {\n if (rule.pattern.test(goalText)) {\n metrics.push({ metric: rule.metric, threshold: rule.threshold, comparator: rule.comparator });\n }\n }\n if (metrics.length === 0) {\n // 默认使用 LLM 评估\n metrics.push({ metric: 'llm', threshold: 0.9, comparator: '>=' });\n }\n return { goalText, metrics };\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 项目快照与回滚\n\n```javascript\n// snapshot.js\nconst fs = require('fs-extra');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nasync function snapshot(projectPath, snapshotId) {\n const snapDir = path.join(projectPath, '.autofix_snapshots', snapshotId);\n await fs.copy(projectPath, snapDir, { filter: src => !src.includes('.autofix_snapshots') });\n return snapDir;\n}\n\nasync function restoreSnapshot(snapDir, projectPath) {\n await fs.remove(projectPath);\n await fs.copy(snapDir, projectPath);\n await fs.remove(snapDir);\n}\n\nasync function cleanupSnapshots(projectPath, keepCount = 3) {\n const snapRoot = path.join(projectPath, '.autofix_snapshots');\n const dirs = await fs.readdir(snapRoot);\n const sorted = dirs.sort((a,b) => fs.statSync(path.join(snapRoot, a)).mtime - fs.statSync(path.join(snapRoot, b)).mtime);\n for (let i = 0; i < sorted.length - keepCount; i++) {\n await fs.remove(path.join(snapRoot, sorted[i]));\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.3 评估模块（量化目标达成度）\n\n```javascript\n// evaluator.js\nconst { exec } = require('child_process');\nconst util = require('util');\nconst execPromise = util.promisify(exec);\n\nasync function evaluate(projectPath, metrics) {\n const results = {};\n for (const m of metrics) {\n switch (m.metric) {\n case 'eslint':\n try {\n const { stdout } = await execPromise(`npx eslint --format json ${projectPath}`);\n const data = JSON.parse(stdout);\n const errorCount = data.reduce((sum, f) => sum + f.errorCount, 0);\n const warningCount = data.reduce((sum, f) => sum + f.warningCount, 0);\n results.eslint = { errorCount, warningCount, pass: errorCount === 0 && warningCount === 0 };\n } catch (e) {\n results.eslint = { errorCount: -1, warningCount: -1, pass: false };\n }\n break;\n case 'test_pass_rate':\n // 假设使用 jest\n const { stdout } = await execPromise(`npx jest --json --outputFile=test-results.json`);\n const testData = JSON.parse(stdout);\n const passRate = testData.numPassedTests / testData.numTotalTests;\n results.test_pass_rate = passRate;\n break;\n case 'llm':\n const llmScore = await askLLM(`根据以下项目摘要，评估是否达成目标: ${metrics[0].goalText}\\n${await getProjectSummary(projectPath)}`);\n results.llm = llmScore;\n break;\n }\n }\n // 计算总体达成度（加权平均）\n let totalScore = 0;\n for (const m of metrics) {\n let value = results[m.metric];\n if (m.comparator === '>=') totalScore += (value >= m.threshold ? 1 : 0);\n else if (m.comparator === '<=') totalScore += (value <= m.threshold ? 1 : 0);\n else if (m.comparator === '==') totalScore += (value === m.threshold ? 1 : 0);\n else if (m.comparator === 'improve_percent') totalScore += (value >= m.threshold ? 1 : 0);\n }\n const finalScore = totalScore / metrics.length;\n return { finalScore, details: results, isMet: finalScore >= 0.9 };\n}\n```\n\n### 2.4 计划生成模块（LLM 驱动）\n\n```javascript\n// planner.js\nasync function generatePlan(projectPath, goal, metrics, previousAttempts) {\n const summary = await getProjectSummary(projectPath); // 文件树 + 关键代码片段\n const prompt = `\n 项目摘要: ${summary}\n 改进目标: ${goal}\n 量化指标: ${JSON.stringify(metrics)}\n 之前尝试过的计划: ${previousAttempts.map(p => p.description).join('; ')}\n 请生成下一步具体的改进计划（JSON 数组），每个动作包含 type, file, description 和可选的代码片段。\n 支持的动作类型: refactor, rename, delete, add, fix_eslint, fix_test。\n 只输出 JSON，不要解释。\n `;\n const response = await callLLM(prompt);\n return JSON.parse(response);\n}\n```\n\n### 2.5 执行模块（安全应用修改）\n\n```javascript\n// executor.js\nasync function applyPlan(plan, projectPath) {\n const backupId = Date.now().toString();\n const backupDir = await snapshot(projectPath, backupId);\n try {\n for (const action of plan) {\n const filePath = path.join(projectPath, action.file);\n switch (action.type) {\n case 'refactor':\n let content = await fs.readFile(filePath, 'utf8');\n content = applyRefactor(content, action.description);\n await fs.writeFile(filePath, content);\n break;\n case 'rename':\n const oldPath = path.join(projectPath, action.oldName);\n const newPath = path.join(projectPath, action.newName);\n await fs.move(oldPath, newPath);\n break;\n case 'fix_eslint':\n await execPromise(`npx eslint --fix ${filePath}`);\n break;\n // 其他动作...\n }\n }\n // 可选：运行测试验证\n const testsPass = await runTests(projectPath);\n if (!testsPass) throw new Error('Tests failed after applying plan');\n return { success: true, backupId };\n } catch (err) {\n await restoreSnapshot(backupDir, projectPath);\n return { success: false, error: err.message };\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 主循环（自主迭代）\n\n```javascript\n// autofix.js\nasync function autoImproveProject(goal, projectPath, maxIterations = 5) {\n const metrics = parseGoal(goal).metrics;\n let iteration = 0;\n let previousPlans = [];\n let bestScore = 0;\n let bestSnapshot = null;\n\n // 初始快照\n const initialSnapshot = await snapshot(projectPath, 'initial');\n\n while (iteration < maxIterations) {\n iteration++;\n console.log(`[AutoFix] 第 ${iteration} 轮迭代`);\n\n // 1. 评估当前状态\n const { finalScore, details, isMet } = await evaluate(projectPath, metrics);\n console.log(`当前达成度: ${finalScore}`);\n if (isMet) {\n console.log(`目标已达成，停止改进`);\n await cleanupSnapshots(projectPath);\n return { success: true, iterations: iteration, finalScore, details };\n }\n\n // 2. 如果分数倒退，回滚到最佳快照\n if (finalScore < bestScore && bestSnapshot) {\n console.log(`分数下降，回滚到最佳版本`);\n await restoreSnapshot(bestSnapshot, projectPath);\n continue;\n }\n if (finalScore > bestScore) {\n bestScore = finalScore;\n bestSnapshot = await snapshot(projectPath, `best_${iteration}`);\n }\n\n // 3. 生成改进计划\n const plan = await generatePlan(projectPath, goal, metrics, previousPlans);\n previousPlans.push({ iteration, description: JSON.stringify(plan) });\n\n // 4. 应用计划\n const result = await applyPlan(plan, projectPath);\n if (!result.success) {\n console.log(`计划执行失败: ${result.error}，跳过本次`);\n continue;\n }\n }\n\n console.log(`达到最大迭代次数 ${maxIterations}，目标未完全达成`);\n return { success: false, iterations: maxIterations, finalScore: bestScore };\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、与 OpenClaw 任务系统集成\n\n### 3.1 意图识别\n\n在反向代理中间件或消息处理中：\n\n```javascript\nif (/自动(化)?改进|自主优化|让系统自己改/i.test(message)) {\n const goal = extractGoal(message);\n const projectPath = detectProjectPath(message); // 或使用当前工作目录\n // 异步启动，不阻塞\n setImmediate(() => autoImproveProject(goal, projectPath));\n return res.json({ message: `自动改进任务已启动，目标: ${goal}` });\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 进度报告（可选）\n\n通过 WebSocket 或消息接口定期向用户推送进度：\n\n```javascript\nasync function reportProgress(iteration, score) {\n await sendUserMessage(`[自动改进] 第 ${iteration} 轮完成，当前达成度 ${score}`);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、五维分析\n\n| 维度 | 实现 | 评价 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **科学性** | 基于目标分解、量化指标、LLM 生成计划、回滚机制，模拟人类迭代改进过程。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **鲁棒性** | 快照回滚、测试验证、分数下降自动恢复；最大迭代次数限制；异常捕获。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **灵活性** | 支持多种预定义指标（ESLint、测试、复杂度）并可扩展；LLM 评估兜底；计划类型可插拔。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **可嵌入性** | 纯函数模块，通过文件系统交互，无外部依赖（除 LLM API）；可轻松集成到 OpenClaw 或其他任务系统。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **效率性** | 增量评估，仅修改必要文件；并行执行独立动作（如多个文件修复）；避免重复全量分析。 | ✅ 高 |\n\n---\n\n## 五、自我审查修正记录\n\n| 版本 | 问题 | 修正 |\n|------|------|------|\n| v0.1 | 没有回滚机制，可能破坏项目 | 增加快照和恢复功能 |\n| v0.2 | 依赖单一 LLM 评估，不稳定 | 增加 ESLint、测试等确定性指标，LLM 仅作兜底 |\n| v0.3 | 未处理计划执行失败 | 增加 try-catch 和回滚，失败后跳过本次继续迭代 |\n| v0.4 | 分数倒退无应对 | 记录最佳快照，分数下降时自动回滚 |\n| v0.5 | 无限循环风险 | 增加最大迭代次数，连续无提升时提前终止 |\n\n---"}],"timestamp":1775380793148}}
{"type":"message","id":"10f599a7","parentId":"84a50c03","timestamp":"2026-04-05T09:19:58.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了一个很详细的需求分析：自动化项目改进系统。这个系统可以：\n1. 接收用户的目标（如\"让代码符合ESLint标准\"）\n2. 自动分析项目当前状态\n3. 生成改进计划\n4. 执行修改5. 评估是否达成目标\n6. 迭代直到达成或达到最大次数\n\n这需要：1. 意图识别\n2. 目标解析\n3. 项目快照/回滚\n4. 评估模块\n5. 计划生成（可能需要LLM）\n6. 执行模块\n7. 主循环这是一个复杂的任务，应该先评分。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_891cf5384d1d4492bd3d5db6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\n// 分析这个任务\nconst task = '实现自动化项目改进系统';\nconst words = task.length;\nconst complexity = Math.ceil(words / 5);\nconst uncertainty = 2; // 需要多个新模块\nconst total = complexity + uncertainty;\nconsole.log('📊 评分:', complexity, '+', uncertainty, '=', total, '/6');\nconsole.log('建议: SPAWN_SUBAGENT (复杂项目)');\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":158374,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158613,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775380793159,"responseId":"chatcmpl-726bf03f-3854-4e5d-b7fe-91f57235be1b"}}
