{"type":"message","id":"6a33af7a","parentId":"ada0af05","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:22:49.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求配置 self-improving 技能。让我根据 SKILL.md 中的说明来设置这个技能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_61a341e1c2674edb9572c60f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 评分\ntask=\"配置 self-improving 技能\"\necho \"📊 评分: 1 + 1 = 2/6 (DIRECT)\"\n\n# 配置 self-improving 目录\necho \"=== 配置 self-improving ===\"\n\n# 创建目录\nmkdir -p ~/self-improving/projects\nmkdir -p ~/self-improving/domains\nmkdir -p ~/self-improving/archive\n\n# 复制模板文件\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/memory.md ~/self-improving/ 2>/dev/null || true\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/corrections.md ~/self-improving/ 2>/dev/null || true\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/learning.md ~/self-improving/ 2>/dev/null || true\n\necho \"目录结构:\"\nls -la ~/self-improving/\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 写入初始记忆 ===\"\ncat > ~/self-improving/memory.md << 'EOF'\n# OpenClaw Self-Improving Memory\n\n## 核心规则\n- 评分后必须等待用户确认才能执行\n- 用户说\"全自动\"或\"直接执行\"时跳过确认\n- 每次纠正立即写入 corrections.md\n- 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## 技能系统\n- v7.0 task-orchestrator (15个模块)\n- auto_improve (6个模块)\n- 意图判断 intent_detector\n- 上下文保护 context_server (18790)\n- Router 反向代理 (3002)\n\n## 用户偏好\n- 深色主题\n- 直接沟通，不拐弯抹角\n\n## 待学习领域\n- WebSocket 对话拦截\n- LLM 集成用于 auto_improve\n\n最后更新: 2026-04-05\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ self-improving 已配置\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":181202,"output":431,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181633,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775384560785,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fbab9f1e-a0d1-4684-91e7-b48999447bac"}}
