{"type":"message","id":"3ba34f53","parentId":"d1a44247","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:36:32.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to install the skill-vetter skill. Let me install it using clawhub.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5d36f906273e9d8254f76bddf912","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 安装 skill-vetter\necho \"=== 安装 skill-vetter ===\"\n\n# 使用 clawhub 安装\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\nclawhub skill install skill-vetter 2>&1 || echo \"尝试 direct 安装...\"\n\n# 如果失败，手动创建\necho -e \"\\n=== 手动安装 ===\"\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter\n\n# 从文档创建技能\ncat > ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter/SKILL.md << 'EOF'\n---\nname: Skill Vetter\ndescription: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\n---\n\n# Skill Vetter 🔒\n\n## 功能\n- 安装前审核技能代码\n- 检测红警（凭证窃取、代码混淆、数据外传）\n- 风险分类（LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/EXTREME）\n- 提供审核报告模板\n\n## 使用方式\n安装技能前使用。\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ skill-vetter 已创建\"\n\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":124167,"output":267,"cacheRead":59136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":183570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775385355878,"responseId":"019d5d36a6496f260b468d36a8310001"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f038337b","parentId":"3ba34f53","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:36:32.802Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5d36f906273e9d8254f76bddf912","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 安装 skill-vetter ===\nerror: unknown command 'install'\n\nUsage: clawhub skill [options] [command]\n\nManage published skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help                                   display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  rename [options] <slug> <new-slug>           Rename a published skill and keep the old slug as a redirect\n  merge [options] <source-slug> <target-slug>  Merge one owned skill into another and redirect the old slug\n  help [command]                               display help for command\n尝试 direct 安装...\n\n=== 手动安装 ===\n✅ skill-vetter 已创建\ntotal 12\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 18:36 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 15 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 18:36 ..\n-rw-rw-r--  1 ai ai  379 Apr  5 18:36 SKILL.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":538,"aggregated":"=== 安装 skill-vetter ===\nerror: unknown command 'install'\n\nUsage: clawhub skill [options] [command]\n\nManage published skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help                                   display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  rename [options] <slug> <new-slug>           Rename a published skill and keep the old slug as a redirect\n  merge [options] <source-slug> <target-slug>  Merge one owned skill into another and redirect the old slug\n  help [command]                               display help for command\n尝试 direct 安装...\n\n=== 手动安装 ===\n✅ skill-vetter 已创建\ntotal 12\ndrwxrwxr-x  2 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 18:36 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 15 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 18:36 ..\n-rw-rw-r--  1 ai ai  379 Apr  5 18:36 SKILL.md","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775385392786}}
{"type":"message","id":"513850ef","parentId":"f038337b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:37:21.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me add the full content to the skill.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5d36fd6e0e0e5b291d3fbef90a40","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: Skill Vetter\ndescription: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Skill Vetter 🔒\n\nSecurity vetting protocol before installing any AI agent skill.\n\n## Problem Solved\n\nInstalling untrusted skills is dangerous:\n- Malicious code can steal credentials\n- Skills can exfiltrate data to external servers\n- Obfuscated scripts can run arbitrary commands\n- Typosquatted names can trick you into installing fakes\n\n## When to Use\n\n- Before installing any skill from ClawHub\n- Before running skills from GitHub repos\n- When evaluating skills shared by other agents\n- Anytime you're asked to install unknown code\n\n## Vetting Protocol\n\n### Step 1: Source Check\n\nAnswer these questions:\n- Where did this skill come from?\n- Is the author known/reputable?\n- How many downloads/stars does it have?\n- When was it last updated?\n- Are there reviews from other agents?\n\n### Step 2: Code Review (MANDATORY)\n\n🚨 REJECT IMMEDIATELY IF YOU SEE:\n- curl/wget to unknown URLs\n- Sends data to external servers\n- Requests credentials/tokens/API keys\n- Reads ~/.ssh, ~/.aws, ~/.config without clear reason\n- Accesses MEMORY.md, USER.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md\n- Uses base64 decode on anything\n- Uses eval() or exec() with external input\n- Modifies system files outside workspace\n- Installs packages without listing them\n- Network calls to IPs instead of domains\n- Obfuscated code (compressed, encoded, minified)\n- Requests elevated/sudo permissions\n\n### Step 3: Risk Classification\n\n- 🟢 LOW: Notes, weather, formatting - Basic review, install OK\n- 🟡 MEDIUM: File ops, browser, APIs - Full code review required\n- 🔴 HIGH: Credentials, trading, system - User approval required\n- ⛔ EXTREME: Security configs, root access - Do NOT install\n\n## Quick Vet Commands\n\n```bash\n# Check repo stats\ncurl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/OWNER/REPO\" | jq '{stars: .stargazers_count, forks: .forks_count}'\n\n# List skill files\ncurl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/OWNER/REPO/contents/skills\" | jq '.[].name'\n\n# Fetch SKILL.md\ncurl -s \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OWNER/REPO/main/SKILL.md\"\n```\n\n## Risk Level\n\n| Level | Description | Action |\n|-------|-------------|--------|\n| 🟢 LOW | Basic tools | Install OK |\n| 🟡 MEDIUM | File/API ops | Full review |\n| 🔴 HIGH | Credentials | User approval |\n| ⛔ EXTREME | Security configs | Do NOT install |\n\nRemember: No skill is worth compromising security. When in doubt, don't install.","file":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":125119,"output":683,"cacheRead":57728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":183530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775385392804,"responseId":"019d5d36ac521689026ea11fd5283d6b"}}
