{"type":"message","id":"22a4e198","parentId":"6c4564aa","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:46:43.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skills don't have skill.js - they're documentation-only. They're not \"executed\" in the traditional sense.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 两个技能都没有自动执行\n\n| 技能 | 有 skill.js | 执行情况 |\n|------|-------------|----------|\n| **skill-vetter** | ❌ 无 | 仅手动参考文档 |\n| **self-improving** | ❌ 无 | 仅手动参考文档 |\n\n**实际情况**：\n- 这两个都是**纯文档模板**\n- 没有代码，不会自动执行\n- 我只是在需要时**手动查阅**这些文档\n\n**如果要让它们自动工作**，需要写 skill.js，但目前没这个必要。\n\n要写代码让它们自动触发吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":184802,"output":142,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":184944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775385997920,"responseId":"chatcmpl-092a3eb8-1d2c-428c-b392-df5df4efff03"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"4c3f4e70","parentId":"22a4e198","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:51:29.918Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\n实现 OpenClaw 全自动任务编排系统 v7.0，包含8大核心模块：评分因子垂直拓展、路由决策、超大任务执行器、上下文保护、子代理进度上报、安全模块、效率优化、部署运维。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 执行任务前必须先评分，评分后等待用户确认才能执行\n- 只删除今天创建的技能及相关测试记忆，保留用户偏好和核心规则\n- 用户说\"全自动化\"或\"直接执行\"时跳过确认步骤\n- 输出用自然语言描述，不使用机械列表格式\n- 使用 intent_detector.js 判断用户消息是\"任务\"还是\"询问\"\n- 意图判断阈值：totalScore >= 1.0 判定为任务\n- 评分维度：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 修复空壳技能：task-weight-estimator、vector-memory 添加完整代码\n- [x] 创建 task_orchestrator/scripts 目录下的模块：scoring.js, context_protector.js, subagent_executor.js\n- [x] 创建 auto-orchestrator 技能（v1.0 - v1.1）\n- [x] 启动保护层 context_server (端口 18790)\n- [x] 删除今天创建的 4 个技能（task-weight-estimator, vector-memory, task_orchestrator, auto-orchestrator）\n- [x] 清理测试记忆，保留用户偏好和核心规则\n- [x] Spawn 子代理实现 v7.0（完成评分模块，356行代码）\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 实现 v7.0 剩余模块（路由决策、上下文保护、分片并行等）\n\n### Blocked\n- 子代理任务超时（运行5分钟后未完成），当前只完成评分模块\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **评分规则**: 每次执行任务前必须使用 task-weight-estimator 评分（复杂度 + 不确定性 = 0-6分），根据总分选择 DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/MULTI_SUBAGENT\n- **集成方案**: 创建 auto-orchestrator 作为前置拦截器，集成 task-weight-estimator + vector-memory + 保护层 context_server\n- **分片并行**: 已确认机器有 12 核 CPU，将使用 Node.js child_process 实现多核并行\n- **自动化例外**: 用户说\"全自动化\"或\"直接执行\"时，跳过确认步骤直接执行\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 让子代理继续完成 v7.0 剩余模块\n2. 实现分片并行模块（使用 child_process 利用12核）\n3. 实现路由决策模块（动态阈值、用户覆盖、配置化规则）\n4. 实现上下文保护模块（token计数、压缩策略）\n5. 与现有保护层 ~/.openclaw/protection/ 集成\n\n## Critical Context\n子代理 session_key: `agent:main:subagent:4ba01455-9f9d-443d-aa2d-1eb6a1af0398` 正在执行 v7.0 实现，但遇到超时问题（5分钟），只完成了评分模块（356行代码）。系统需要继续实现剩余模块。\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n- **评分流程**: 每次执行任务前必须评分，评分后等待用户确认才能执行，除非用户明确说\"全自动\"或\"直接执行\"\n- **意图判断**: 先用 intent_detector.js 判断用户消息是\"任务\"还是\"询问\"，如果是询问则不需要评分直接回答\n- **输出优化**: 评分后用自然语言描述（如\"需要执行任务(1.6分)，简单任务，直接执行\"），去掉1.2.3.列表\n- **自动化例外**: 用户说\"全自动化\"或\"直接执行\"时，跳过确认步骤直接执行\n\n## Open TODOs\n- WebSocket对话拦截未实现（当前只支持HTTP拦截，Gateway使用WebSocket通信）\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 核心规则：评分 → 等待确认 → 执行\n- 自动化规则：用户说\"全自动化\"/\"直接执行\"时跳过确认\n- 输出规则：自然语言描述，不使用机械列表格式\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户说\"进行全自动化操作\"，已确认自动化规则生效\n- 用户问\"能不能按照我的需求，把应该项目自动化改成我的需求\"，已更新记忆\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **技能目录**: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/\n- **模块文件**: scoring.js, mega_executor.js, context_protector.js, progress_reporter.js, security.js, optimizer.js, openclaw-router.js, intent_detector.js, quick_score.js\n- **记忆文件**: ~/.openclaw/vector_memory.json\n- **端口**: 3002 (Router), 18789 (Gateway), 18790 (context_server), 18791 (health)\n- **Gateway PID**: 5583\n- **对话拦截路径**: /agent, /chat, /api/chat/send, /api/message/send, /api/v1/chat, /webhook\n- **意图判断阈值**: 1.0 (totalScore >= 1.0判定为任务)\n- **评分维度**: logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n- **路由模式**: DIRECT (0-2分), STEP_ARCHIVE (3-5分), SPAWN_SUBAGENT (6-8分), MEGA_TASK (>8分)\n- **子代理 session_key**: agent:main:subagent:4ba01455-9f9d-443d-aa2d-1eb6a1af0398\n- **CPU**: 12核 (6核 × 2线程)\n- **内存**: 15GB (可用 12GB)\n- **核心规则记忆 ID**: 1775371000001-commitment\n- **用户偏好记忆**: 用户偏好深色主题\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Decisions\n- 子代理任务“auto-improve-system”已启动，正在创建自动化项目改进系统的各个模块\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 子代理任务超时（1m56s），需要恢复或重新启动自动化项目改进系统的工作\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 保持内部细节私密（不提及系统/日志/会话详情）\n- 将结果转换为正常助手语气后发送\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户请求将子代理结果转换为助手风格并发送\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- session_key: agent:main:subagent:f9094f43-0ca3-4679-9ce2-a77a60bc9984\n- session_id: d571c5d8-52e7-4cec-92c1-5c3edb3f3fba\n- task: auto-improve-system\n- status: timed out\n- runtime: 1m56s\n- tokens: 41.5k (in 38.0k / out 3.5k)\n- result: \"我来创建自动化项目改进系统的各个模块。\"\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 17:13 GMT+8] 我是问你，能不能把一个项目一直改，改成我想要的效果，再停止\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 评分: 0 (非任务)\n- Assistant: (询问，不需要评分)\n\n---\n\n**目前做不到**。\n\n现在的能力是：\n- 一次性任务：执行 → 完成\n- 迭代式改进：改 → 给你看 → 继续改 → 给你看 → ... → 停止\n\n**你问的是后者**。\n\n要实现这个功能，需要：\n1. 接收目标描述\n2. 执行修改\n3. 返回结果让你确认\n4. 根据你的反馈继续或停止\n\n要我实现这个\"迭代式项目改进\"模式吗？\n\n🦐\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 17:19 GMT+8] 分析一下：# 自动化项目改进系统（自主迭代，无需人工确认）最优解 v1.0\n\n> 用户只需提供**最终目标**（例如“重构 `src/` 目录，使代码符合 ESLint 标准且所有测试通过”），系统自动执行多轮分析、计划、修改、评估，直到目标达成或达到最大迭代次数。 \n> **五维设计**：科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性。 \n> **无需人工干预**：完全自主运行。\n\n---\n\n## 一、系统架构\n\n```\n用户目标 → 项目快照 → 迭代循环\n │\n ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐\n │ │ │\n 分析模块 计划模块 执行模块\n (评估当前状态) (生成改进动作) (应用修改+测试)\n │ │ │\n └───────────────┼───────────────┘\n │\n 评估模块\n (检查目标达成度)\n │\n 未达成 → 继续迭代（最多 N 次）\n 达成 → 输出最终结果\n```\n\n所有模块均为无状态函数，通过共享工作区（项目路径）和检查点文件持久化状态。\n...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 📊 评分: 3 + 2 = 5 /6\n建议: SPAWN_SUBAGENT (复杂项目)\n- Assistant: 📊 评分: 5/6 (SPAWN_SUBAGENT - 复杂项目)\n\n---\n\n## 分析\n\n**可以做**，而且方案很完整。\n\n**核心模块**：\n| 模块 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| goalParser | 目标解析（ESLint/测试/复杂度） |\n| snapshot | 项目快照+回滚 |\n| evaluator | 评估达成度 |\n| planner | LLM生成改进计划 |\n| executor | 安全执行修改 |\n| autofix | 主循环迭代 |\n\n**能力**：\n- 接收目标如\"让代码符合ESLint标准\"\n- 自动迭代改进，最多N轮\n- 失败自动回滚\n- 无需人工确认\n\n**需要**：\n- CodingPlan/DeepSeek API（生成计划）\n- 项目目录访问权限\n- 多次迭代执行\n\n要实现吗？🦐\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 17:20 GMT+8] 实现\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (sessions_spawn): {\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:f9094f43-0ca3-4679-9ce2-a77a60bc9984\",\n  \"runId\": \"d9399feb-7f6a-40bf-942c-6741ad73b409\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (sessions_yield): {\n  \"status\": \"yielded\",\n  \"message\": \"Turn yielded.\"\n}","firstKeptEntryId":"7d05dc8a","tokensBefore":184944,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
{"type":"message","id":"bacd3044","parentId":"4c3f4e70","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:51:29.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 18:49 GMT+8] 学习、安装：适用于 Openclaw 的 Superpowers AI 编码工作流\n￼\n一种强制性的、规范优先的 TDD 工作流，利用子代理进行头脑风暴、规划并执行稳健的软件开发任务。\nwlshlad85\nv1.0.0\n2026年2月28日\n3\n2.6k\n24\n安装\n基本信息\nSkill.md\n安装与下载\n1. ClawHub CLI\n从源直接安装技能的最快方式。\nnpx clawhub@latest install superpowers\n￼\n2. 手动安装\n将技能文件夹复制到以下位置之一\n全局模式\n~/.openclaw/skills/\n￼\n工作区\n<project>/skills/\n￼\n优先级：工作区 > 本地 > 内置\n3. 提示词安装\n将此提示词复制到 OpenClaw 即可自动安装。\n请帮我使用 Clawhub 安装 superpowers。如果尚未安装 Clawhub，请先安装（npm i -g clawhub）。\n￼\n￼\n更倾向于下载？\n获取包含原生技能文件的ZIP压缩包。\n￼\n下载技能 (.zip)\n什么是 Superpowers AI 编码工作流？\nSuperpowers 是一个全面的开发框架，旨在改变 AI 代理构建软件的方式。通过强制执行从最初头脑风暴到最终分支合并的严格流程，该技能确保每一段代码都有设计文档支持，并通过测试驱动开发（TDD）进行验证。它是 Openclaw Skills 中最强大的技能之一，适合希望通过结构化子代理委派来提高生产力的开发者。\n该工作流通过设立硬性门槛来防止技术债务：在设计获得批准之前不编写任何代码，在没有失败的测试之前不实现任何功能。这种系统化的方法通过利用处理实现和多阶段审查的子代理驱动构建循环，确保了复杂项目的高质量输出。\nSuperpowers AI 编码工作流 应用场景\n使用结构化流水线从头开发新应用程序或功能。\n通过系统化的根本原因调查解决复杂的 Bug 或测试失败。\n编排多个子代理以同时处理实现和代码审查。\n管理功能分支的端到端生命周期，包括验证和 PR 创建。\nSuperpowers AI 编码工作流 工作原理\n1. 启动：分析项目背景并进行方案头脑风暴，提供 2-3 个权衡方案。\n2. 文档化：在 docs/plans 目录中创建正式设计文档并获得用户批准。\n3. 规划：将获批的设计分解为实施计划中耗时 2-5 分钟的 TDD 任务。\n4. 执行：使用 sessions_spawn 为每个任务分派实现子代理，随后由规范和质量审查员进行审查。\n5. 验证：确认所有测试通过并进行最终的全面代码审查。\n6. 完成：通过本地合并或推送已完成功能的拉取请求来完成分支。\nSuperpowers AI 编码工作流 配置指南\n确保您的环境支持 exec 工具和会话生成（session spawning）功能，以充分利用这些 Openclaw Skills。\n# 在您的环境中初始化 Superpowers 技能\nmkdir -p docs/plans\n# 确保 agent 配置中可以使用 exec 和 sessions_spawn 工具\nSuperpowers AI 编码工作流 数据架构与分类体系\n文件路径\n描述\n元数据/内容\ndocs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md\n高层设计文档\n项目背景、权衡方案和获批架构。\ndocs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<feature>.md\n实施计划\n耗时 2-5 分钟的逐步 TDD 任务。\nsessions_spawn 日志\n子代理元数据\n任务背景、文件路径、约束和验证步骤。\nSuperpowers AI 编码工作流 高级特性\n用于并行实现和多阶段代码审查的自动化子代理分派。\n系统化的四阶段调试协议，在尝试修复前识别根本原因。\n集成分支管理，用于自动化 PR 创建和本地合并。\n强制性 TDD 执行，确保在存在失败测试之前绝不编写代码。\nSKILL.md\n￼\nname: superpowers\ndescription: >\n Spec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow. Use when:\n (1) building any new feature or app — triggers brainstorm → plan → subagent execution loop,\n (2) debugging a bug or test failure — triggers systematic root-cause process,\n (3) user says \"let's build\", \"help me plan\", \"I want to add X\", or \"this is broken\",\n (4) completing a feature branch — triggers test verification + merge/PR options.\n NOT for: one-liner fixes (just edit), reading code, or non-code tasks.\n Requires exec tool and sessions_spawn.\nSuperpowers — OpenClaw Edition\nAdapted from obra/superpowers. Mandatory workflow — not suggestions.\nThe Pipeline\nIdea → Brainstorm → Plan → Subagent-Driven Build (TDD) → Code Review → Finish Branch\nEvery coding task follows this pipeline. \"Too simple to need a design\" is always wrong.\n￼\nPhase 1: Brainstorming\nTrigger: User wants to build something. Activate before touching any code.\nSee: references/brainstorming.md\nSummary:\nExplore project context (files, docs, recent commits)\nAsk clarifying questions — one at a time, prefer multiple choice\nPropose 2–3 approaches with trade-offs + recommendation\nPresent design in sections, get approval after each\nWrite design doc → docs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md → commit\nHand off to Phase 2: Writing Plans\nHARD GATE: Do NOT write any code until user approves design.\n￼\nPhase 2: Writing Plans\nTrigger: Design approved. Activated by brainstorming phase.\nSee: references/writing-plans.md\nSummary:\nWrite a detailed task-by-task implementation plan\nEach task = 2–5 minutes: write test → watch fail → implement → watch pass → commit\nSave to docs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<feature>.md\nAnnounce: \"I'm using the writing-plans skill to create the implementation plan.\"\nAfter saving, offer two execution modes:\nSubagent-driven (current session): sessions_spawn per task + two-stage review\nManual execution: User runs tasks themselves\n￼\nPhase 3: Subagent-Driven Development\nTrigger: Plan exists, user chooses subagent-driven execution.\nSee: references/subagent-development.md\nPer-task loop (OpenClaw):\nsessions_spawn an implementer subagent with task + full plan context\nWait for completion announcement\nsessions_spawn a spec-reviewer subagent → must confirm code matches spec\nsessions_spawn a code-quality reviewer subagent → must approve quality\nFix any issues, re-review if needed\nMark task done, move to next\nFinal: dispatch overall code reviewer → hand off to Phase 5\nTDD is mandatory in every task. See references/tdd.md.\n￼\nPhase 4: Systematic Debugging\nTrigger: Bug, test failure, unexpected behaviour — any technical issue.\nSee: references/systematic-debugging.md\nHARD GATE: No fixes without root cause investigation first.\nFour phases:\nRoot Cause Investigation (read errors, reproduce, check recent changes, trace data flow)\nPattern Analysis (find working examples, compare, identify differences)\nHypothesis + Testing (one hypothesis at a time, test to prove/disprove)\nFix + Verification (fix at root, not symptom; verify fix doesn't break anything)\n￼\nPhase 5: Finishing a Branch\nTrigger: All tasks complete, all tests pass.\nSee: references/finishing-branch.md\nSummary:\nVerify all tests pass\nDetermine base branch\nPresent 4 options: merge locally / push + PR / keep / discard\nExecute choice\nClean up\n￼\nOpenClaw Subagent Dispatch Pattern\nWhen dispatching implementer or reviewer subagents, use sessions_spawn:\nGoal: [one sentence]\nContext: [why it matters, which plan file]\nFiles: [exact paths]\nConstraints: [what NOT to do — no scope creep, TDD only]\nVerify: [how to confirm success — tests pass, specific command]\nTask text: [paste full task from plan]\nRun sessions_spawn with the task as a detailed prompt. The sub-agent announces results automatically.\n￼\nKey Principles\nOne question at a time during brainstorm\nTDD always — write failing test first, delete code written before tests\nYAGNI — remove unnecessary features from all designs\nDRY — no duplication\nSystematic over ad-hoc — follow the process especially under time pressure\nEvidence over claims — verify before declaring success\nFrequent commits — after each green test"}],"timestamp":1775386289919}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7db1392","parentId":"bacd3044","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:51:39.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户分享了 superpowers 技能的描述，这是一个强制性的 TDD 工作流技能。让我评分并安装它。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n📊 评分: 2 + 1 = 3/6 (STEP_ARCHIVE)\n\n---\n\n## Superpowers AI 编码工作流\n\n这是一个**强大的开发框架**：\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **TDD工作流** | 测试驱动开发 |\n| **子代理驱动** | sessions_spawn 并行实现 |\n| **四阶段调试** | 根本原因分析 |\n| **分支管理** | 自动 PR 创建 |\n\n**工作流程**：\n```\nIdea → 头脑风暴 → 设计文档 → 实施计划 → 子代理执行 → 代码审查 → 完成分支\n```\n\n等待确认是否安装？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":76375,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76534,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775386289927,"responseId":"chatcmpl-28cf0aa7-7d82-45be-996e-d7ef6304f889"}}
