{"type":"message","id":"553dd751","parentId":"6f4542aa","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:04:50.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了一个看起来像是 Vercel Token 的字符串。这是一个 Vercel API Token，格式看起来类似。\n\n不过根据 skill-vetter 的规则，我不应该直接使用或存储用户的敏感凭证。另外，这也可能是用户在测试系统或者是某种形式的验证。\n\n我应该：\n1. 不保存这个 token\n2. 提醒用户不要在聊天中分享敏感凭证\n3. 告诉用户如何在安全的环境变量中设置\n\n让我用自然的方式回应。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这是一个 **Vercel Token**。\n\n**警告**：不要在聊天中直接分享 Token，有安全风险。\n\n**正确设置方式**（在终端执行，不是这里）：\n```bash\n# 临时设置（当前终端有效）\nexport VERCEL_TOKEN=\"vcp_433bpQl6nZ46Xp5GfwamonPDQTrwfRhPWLJp26duUyB94E888H13mDu2\"\n\n# 永久设置（添加到 ~/.bashrc）\necho 'export VERCEL_TOKEN=\"vcp_433bpQl6nZ46Xp5GfwamonPDQTrwfRhPWLJp26duUyB94E888H13mDu2\"' >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n设置后就可以用 vercel-deploy 了。要测试一下吗？\n\n🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2612,"output":259,"cacheRead":79872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82743,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775387073097,"responseId":"019d5d50d107e2340b2bdfb3b90c57fd"}}
