{"type":"message","id":"cc61a0ba","parentId":"084fb551","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:54:20.418Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_683887077ed54422a46d254e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Superpowers 工作流启动 ===\n\n项目: 番茄小说创作助手\n位置: /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/\n\n=== 现有项目分析 ===\ntotal 516\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 31 13:41 -p\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:47 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 ..\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:51 .ai-context\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 .cursor\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 .novel-assistant\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 AAA\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   8863 Mar 30 13:19 AI_NOVEL_ASSISTANT_SUMMARY.md\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai  10922 Mar 30 13:23 USER_GUIDE.md\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 13:38 assets\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:53 bin\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:51 characters\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 data\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   1632 Mar 30 20:35 demo.html\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai    261 Mar 31 19:50 fix-tools.bat\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 lib\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 memory-bank\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 my-novel\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:43 my-novel-tools\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:46 node_modules\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:51 notes\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:47 novel-desktop-app\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 493971 Apr  3 17:40 package-lock.json\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai    839 Apr  3 01:15 package.json\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:51 plots\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 13:38 public\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai      0 Mar 30 21:57 response.txt\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 12:51 settings\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai    151 Mar 30 18:24 simple-test.html\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Apr  5 19:47 src\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai    113 Mar 30 22:53 test-static.html\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai    148 Mar 30 21:48 test.html\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   4096 Mar 30 23:38 types\n\n=== package.json ===\n{\"devDependencies\":{\"@ant-design/icons\":\"^6.1.1\",\"@testing-library/jest-dom\":\"^6.9.1\",\"@testing-library/react\":\"^16.3.2\",\"@types/js-yaml\":\"^4.0.9\",\"@types/node\":\"^25.5.0\",\"@types/react\":\"^19.2.14\",\"@types/react-dom\":\"^19.2.3\",\"@vitejs/plugin-react\":\"^4.0.4\",\"@vitest/ui\":\"^4.1.2\",\"electron\":\"^41.1.0\",\"electron-builder\":\"^26.8.1\",\"esbuild\":\"^0.24.2\",\"jsdom\":\"^29.0.1\",\"nodemon\":\"^3.1.14\",\"npm-run-all\":\"^4.1.5\",\"typescript\":\"^6.0.2\",\"vite\":\"^4.3.9\",\"vitest\":\"^4.1.2\"},\"dependencies\":{\"@electron-toolkit/utils\":\"^4.0.0\",\"@xenova/transformers\":\"^2.17.2\",\"antd\":\"^6.3.4\",\"axios\":\"^1.14.0\",\"echarts\":\"^6.0.0\",\"echarts-for-react\":\"^3.0.6\",\"electron-store\":\"^11.0.2\",\"graphology\":\"^0.26.0\",\"graphology-metrics\":\"^2.4.0\",\"js-yaml\":\"^4.1.1\",\"monaco-editor\":\"^0.55.1\",\"react\":\"^19.2.4\",\"react-dom\":\"^19.2.4\",\"vectra\":\"^0.12.3\",\"zustand\":\"^5.0.12\"}}\n=== 主要源码 ===\nmain\nrenderer\n\n=== 文档 ===\n# AI小说创作助手 - 方案与实现总结\r\n\r\n## 一、方案概述\r\n\r\n### 1.1 核心架构理念\r\n- **极简存储**：所有数据用文件夹和纯文本文件（Markdown + YAML）保存，无需数据库。\r\n- **工具即脚本**：AI生成、情节规划、人格分析等封装为独立命令行工具，按需调用。\r\n- **记忆靠目录**：文件夹层级自然形成情节结构，文件名和元数据提供索引。\r\n- **幻觉靠上下文**：工具运行时自动读取相关文件，构建完整上下文传递给AI。\r\n- **个人使用**：不涉及协作、权限、实时同步，所有数据本地存储，工具离线可用。\r\n\r\n### 1.2 文件组织规范\r\n```\r\nmy-novel/                       # 小说项目根目录\r\n├── project.yaml                # 项目元数据\r\n├── characters/                 # 人物文件夹\r\n├── plots/                      # 情节文件夹\r\n├── settings/                   # 世界观设定文件夹\r\n├── relationships.yaml          # 人物关系索引\r\n├── notes/                      # 个人笔记（可选）\r\n└── .ai-context/                # AI上下文缓存（自动生成）\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 1.3 技术栈\r\n- **运行时**：Node.js\r\n- **命令行框架**：Commander.js\r\n- **文件解析**：js-yaml, marked\r\n- **AI集成**：Axios (支持DeepSeek、OpenAI等)\r\n- **数据格式**：YAML (配置), JSON (静态数据), Markdown (章节内容)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":68,"aggregated":"=== Superpowe