{"type":"message","id":"0710f628","parentId":"7034da65","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:54:37.407Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5d7dd933522fdbb82d856f86f137","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 项目技术栈 ===\n运行时: Electron + Node.js\n前端: React 19 + TypeScript + antd\n编辑器: Monaco Editor\n构建: Vite + electron-builder\n\n=== 现有目录结构 ===\ntotal 0\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Mar 30 13:38 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 ..\ntotal 0\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 ..\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 src\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   60 Mar 30 22:22 test-renderer.html\n\n=== 现有功能模块 ===\ndata\nbin\nlib\nnode_modules\npackage-lock.json\npackage.json\n我的小说"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":51,"aggregated":"=== 项目技术栈 ===\n运行时: Electron + Node.js\n前端: React 19 + TypeScript + antd\n编辑器: Monaco Editor\n构建: Vite + electron-builder\n\n=== 现有目录结构 ===\ntotal 0\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Mar 30 13:38 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 ..\ntotal 0\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 ..\ndrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 4096 Apr  5 19:47 src\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai   60 Mar 30 22:22 test-renderer.html\n\n=== 现有功能模块 ===\ndata\nbin\nlib\nnode_modules\npackage-lock.json\npackage.json\n我的小说","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775390077398}}
{"type":"message","id":"f69868d0","parentId":"0710f628","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:55:08.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"项目目前结构比较简单，src/main 和 src/renderer 都是空的。需要做大量工作。现在我需要提供方案供用户选择。\n\n根据用户的方案，我提供2-3个实现方案：\n1. 方案A：完全按用户方案实现（SQLite + 多模型）\n2. 方案B：渐进式增强（保留现有文件结构，增强AI能力）\n3. 方案C：轻量级实现（使用现有的文件存储，减少后端复杂度）\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🔥 Phase 1: 头脑风暴\n\n**项目背景**：已有 Electron + React 项目框架，但功能较简单\n\n### 现有技术栈\n- Electron + React 19 + TypeScript\n- antd UI 组件\n- Monaco Editor\n- 已有目录结构（characters/, plots/, settings/）\n\n### 你的需求核心\n1. 事实台账（记忆一致性）\n2. AI 多模型分工\n3. 统一创作工作台\n\n---\n\n## 提供三个方案\n\n| 方案 | 复杂度 | 数据存储 | AI模型 | 适合 |\n|------|--------|----------|--------|------|\n| **A: 完整版** | 高 | SQLite | 豆包+DeepSeek | 功能完整、长期维护 |\n| **B: 渐进版** | 中 | 文件+YAML | 现有 | 快速落地、逐步迭代 |\n| **C: 轻量版** | 低 | 纯文件 | 单模型 | 快速见效、最小改动 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐方案 A**（符合你的最终方案），但需要确认：\n\n1. **数据存储**：SQLite 事实台账 + 文件系统，是否接受？\n2. **AI 集成**：需要你提供豆包 API Key 才能接入\n3. **分阶段实施**：先实现工作台 UI，还是先实现事实台账？\n\n你觉得这个方向可以吗？或者你有其他想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":97184,"output":382,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97822,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775390077408,"responseId":"019d5d7eb3927f05c6cde48c19f246a0"}}
