{"type":"message","id":"968f736e","parentId":"471625d2","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:57:58.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Design document is created. Now I need to:\n1. Create implementation plan (Phase 2: Writing Plans)\n2. Execute with subagents\n\nLet me create the detailed implementation plan.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5d809b2ae2d7a316071f37e1c58f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Phase 2: 创建实施计划\nPROJECT_DIR=\"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$PROJECT_DIR/docs/plans\"\n\ncat > \"$PROJECT_DIR/docs/plans/2026-04-05-implementation.md\" << 'EOF'\n# 番茄小说创作助手 - 实施计划\n\n## 任务拆分（每个任务 2-5 分钟，TDD）\n\n### Phase 1: 基础框架\n\n#### Task 1.1: 完善 Electron 主进程\n```\n步骤：创建 main/index.ts\n- 窗口管理\n- IPC 处理器注册\n- 文件系统 API\n- SQLite 连接\n```\n\n#### Task 1.2: 工作台基础 UI\n```\n步骤：创建 renderer/components/Workbench.tsx\n- 三栏布局\n- 响应式设计\n- 基础状态管理\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: 编辑器集成\n\n#### Task 2.1: Monaco Editor 集成\n```\n步骤：创建 Editor 组件\n- 语言支持 Markdown\n- 主题支持\n- 快捷键绑定\n```\n\n#### Task 2.2: 大纲树组件\n```\n步骤：创建 OutlineTree 组件\n- 读取 plots/ 目录\n- 树形展示\n- 双击打开章节\n```\n\n#### Task 2.3: 自动保存\n```\n步骤：实现保存逻辑\n- 防抖 5 秒\n- 手动保存 Ctrl+S\n- 备份保留 10 个版本\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: 事实台账\n\n#### Task 3.1: SQLite 集成\n```\n步骤：创建 db/index.ts\n- better-sqlite3 集成\n- 表结构初始化\n- CRUD 操作\n```\n\n#### Task 3.2: 事实提取服务\n```\n步骤：创建 services/factExtractor.ts\n- 调用 AI 分析章节\n- 解析 JSON 事实\n- 写入数据库\n```\n\n#### Task 3.3: 事实展示面板\n```\n步骤：创建 FactsPanel 组件\n- 按类型筛选\n- 章节关联\n- 点击跳转\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: AI 工具\n\n#### Task 4.1: 多模型服务\n```\n步骤：创建 services/aiModels.ts\n- 豆包 API 封装\n- DeepSeek API 封装\n- 模型选择逻辑\n```\n\n#### Task 4.2: 智能续写\n```\n步骤：创建续写功能\n- 获取光标前 500 字符\n- 流式生成\n- 预览和应用\n```\n\n#### Task 4.3: 逻辑校验\n```\n步骤：创建校验功能\n- 调用 Reasoner\n- 检测战力/逻辑矛盾\n- 给出修改建议\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: 打包发布\n\n#### Task 5.1: 构建配置\n```\n步骤：完善 electron-builder 配置\n- 应用图标\n- 签名配置\n- 更新机制\n```\n\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 实施计划已创建\"\ncat \"$PROJECT_DIR/docs/plans/2026-04-05-implementation.md\" | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1215,"output":695,"cacheRead":97536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775390246447,"responseId":"019d5d808c012dda34f0262608945b2b"}}
