{"type":"message","id":"da37e691","parentId":"44926d66","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:26:58.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经创建了很多核心文件。现在让我给用户一个进度总结，并询问是否继续。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 实施进度\n\n### 已完成\n\n| Phase | 任务 | 状态 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| **Phase 1** | Electron 主进程 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 1** | Preload 脚本 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 2** | 工作台 UI (三栏) | ✅ |\n| **Phase 2** | 大纲树组件 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 2** | 编辑器组件 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 3** | SQLite 事实台账 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 4** | AI 模型服务 | ✅ |\n| **Phase 4** | 事实提取服务 | ✅ |\n\n### 已创建文件\n```\nsrc/\n├── main/index.ts          # Electron 主进程 (96行)\n├── preload/index.ts       # 预加载脚本\n└── renderer/src/\n    ├── App.tsx            # 主应用\n    ├── App.css            # 样式\n    ├── components/\n    │   └── Workbench.tsx  # 工作台组件\n    ├── db/\n    │   └── index.ts       # 事实台账\n    └── services/\n        ├── aiModels.ts    # AI 模型服务\n        └── factExtractor.ts # 事实提取\n```\n\n### 待完成\n- Vite 配置更新\n- 构建配置\n- Monaco Editor 完整集成\n- 打包发布\n\n**需要配置 API Key** 才能使用 AI 功能（豆包/DeepSeek）\n\n要继续完善哪些部分？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":107329,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107655,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775392013966,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6d658e96-c5e3-46fc-a43f-854e27774758"}}
