{"type":"message","id":"fd05e2ba","parentId":"ca5c4e46","timestamp":"2026-04-05T12:33:06.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了大部分功能。让我总结给用户。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ Phase 1-4 核心功能已完成！\n\n### 创建的文件 (11个)\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── main/index.ts           # Electron 主进程\n├── preload/index.ts        # 预加载\n└── renderer/\n    ├── index.html\n    └── src/\n        ├── App.tsx         # 主应用\n        ├── App.css         # 样式\n        ├── main.tsx        # 入口\n        ├── components/\n        │   ├── Editor.tsx     # Monaco 编辑器\n        │   └── Workbench.tsx  # 工作台组件\n        ├── db/\n        │   └── index.ts       # 事实台账\n        ├── services/\n        │   ├── aiModels.ts       # AI 模型服务\n        │   └── factExtractor.ts  # 事实提取\n        └── stores/\n            └── index.ts       # 状态管理\n```\n\n### 完成的功能\n- ✅ 三栏工作台布局\n- ✅ 大纲树（自动读取 plots 目录）\n- ✅ Monaco Editor（Markdown）\n- ✅ 自动保存（5秒防抖）+ Ctrl+S\n- ✅ AI 工具面板\n- ✅ 事实台账架构\n- ✅ 多模型服务（豆包+DeepSeek）\n- ✅ Vite + Electron 构建配置\n\n### 下一步\n1. 配置 API Key\n2. 运行 `npm install` 安装依赖\n3. 测试运行 `npm run dev`\n\n要继续测试运行吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":113240,"output":305,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775392357928,"responseId":"019d5da17487b0f55fdb1ece54a55813"}}
